== 派拉蒙动画短片 ==
超人首度现身大银幕是在[[派拉蒙電影|派拉蒙電影]]发行的一系列动画短片中，每部长度约为10分钟，从1941到1943年间一共制作了17部《[[超人_(1940年代动画)|超人]]》动画片，其中9部由[[弗莱舍工作室|弗莱舍工作室]]（{{lang|en|Fleischer Studios}}）制作，8部由派拉蒙旗下的[[菲默斯工作室|菲默斯工作室]]（{{lang|en|Famous Studios}}）制作<ref name="BarrierBug">{{cite book | last = Barrier | first = Michael | year = 1999 | title = Hollywood Cartoons | url = https://archive.org/details/hollywoodcartoon00barr | location = New York | publisher = Oxford University Press | pages = [https://archive.org/details/hollywoodcartoon00barr/page/303 303]-305 | isbn = 0-19-516729-5}}</ref>。

== 早期真人电影作品 ==
[[哥伦比亚电影公司|哥伦比亚电影公司]]于1948年1月5日发行的15段式系列影集《{{le|超人 (系列影集)|Superman (serial)|超人}}》是首部由真人扮演超人的电影作品<ref name="GMS">{{cite book | last = Harmon | first = Jim | coauthors= Donald F. Glut | title = The Great Movie Serials: Their Sound and Fury | url = https://archive.org/details/greatmovieserial0000harm | origyear = 1973 | publisher = Routledge | isbn = 978-0-7130-0097-9 |pages = [https://archive.org/details/greatmovieserial0000harm/page/206 206]–215 | chapter = 9. The Superheroes "Could Superman Knock Out Captain Marvel"}}</ref>，下一次则是1950年的另一部15段式系列影集《{{link-en|原子人大战超人|Atom Man vs. Superman}}》<ref name="GMS">{{cite book | last = Harmon | first = Jim | coauthors= Donald F. Glut | title = The Great Movie Serials: Their Sound and Fury | url = https://archive.org/details/greatmovieserial0000harm | origyear = 1973 | publisher = Routledge | isbn = 978-0-7130-0097-9 |pages = [https://archive.org/details/greatmovieserial0000harm/page/206 206]–215 | chapter = 9. The Superheroes "Could Superman Knock Out Captain Marvel"}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0042211/ | title = Atom Man vs_ Superman (1950) | work = [[互联网电影数据库|IMDb.com]] | publisher = [[亚马逊公司|Amazon.com]] | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130714060925/http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0042211/ | accessdate = 2014-08-27 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2013-07-14 }}</ref>。之后超人又在1951年的超级英雄电影《超人与摩尔人》中现身，该片由李·施瓦姆（{{lang|en|Lee Sholem}}）执导，巴尼·萨瑞克（{{lang|en|Barney Sarecky}}）监制，[[乔治·里弗斯|乔治·里弗斯]]扮演超人，{{link-en|菲莉斯·科特斯|Phyllis Coates}}饰演路易丝·莱恩，片长58分钟<ref>{{cite web | deadurl = no | url = http://www.tcm.com/tcmdb/title/91977/Superman-and-the-Mole-Men/ | title = Superman and the Mole Men (1951) | publisher = [[透纳娱乐公司|Turner Entertainment]] | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140827011800/http://www.tcm.com/tcmdb/title/91977/Superman-and-the-Mole-Men/ | accessdate = 2014-08-27 | archivedate = 2014-08-27 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0044091/ | title = Superman and the Mole-Men (1951) | work = [[互联网电影数据库|IMDb.com]] | publisher = [[亚马逊公司|Amazon.com]] | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130714034626/http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0044091/ | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2013-07-14 | accessdate = 2014-08-27 }}</ref>。

== 克里斯托弗·里夫系列（1978至1987年） ==
=== 《超人》（1978年） ===
{{Main|超人 (电影)}}
制片人伊利亚·塞尔金德早在1973年时就有了拍摄超人题材电影的设想，说服自己的父亲亚历山大·塞尔金德于1974年11月买下超人的电影版权。两人请来[[马里奥·普佐|马里奥·普佐]]连续撰写两部电影的剧本<ref name="life">{{cite book| author = Julius Schwartz; Brian M. Thomsen | title = Man of Two Worlds: My Life In Science Fiction and Comics | url = https://archive.org/details/manoftwoworldsmy00schw | publisher = HarperCollins | year = 2000 | location = [[纽约|New York City]] | pages = [https://archive.org/details/manoftwoworldsmy00schw/page/135 135]–142 | isbn = 0-380-81051-4| chapter = B.O.}}</ref>，并一度打算找[[史蒂文·斯皮尔伯格|史蒂文·斯皮尔伯格]]担任导演，但亚历山大觉得还是等斯皮尔伯格执导的《[[大白鲨_(电影)|大白鲨]]》上映后看看情况，《大白鲨》上映后大获成功，两位制片人于是联系了斯皮尔伯格，但后者这时已经决定拍摄《[[第三类接触_(电影)|第三类接触]]》<ref name="one on one">{{cite news | author = Barry M. Freiman | title = One-on-One Interview with Producer Ilya Salkind | publisher = Superman Homepage | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140704005928/http://www.supermanhomepage.com/movies/movies.php?topic=interview-salkind | archivedate = 2014-07-04 | url = http://www.supermanhomepage.com/movies/movies.php?topic=interview-salkind | accessdate = 2014-08-27 }}</ref>。{{lang|en|DC}}漫画曾希望由[[穆罕默德·阿里|穆罕默德·阿里]]、[[艾尔·帕西诺|艾尔·帕西诺]]、[[詹姆斯·凯恩|詹姆斯·凯恩]]、[[史蒂夫·麦奎因|史蒂夫·麦奎因]]、[[克林·伊斯威特|克林特·伊斯特伍德]]和[[德斯汀·荷夫曼|达斯汀·霍夫曼]]出演超人<ref name="saga">Richard Donner, Tom Mankiewicz, Ilya Salkind, Pierre Spengler, David Prowse, ''You Will Believe: The Cinematic Saga of Superman'', 2006, Warner Home Video</ref>，[[弗朗西斯·科波拉|弗朗西斯·福特·科波拉]]、[[威廉·弗莱德金|威廉·弗莱德金]]、[[彼得·葉慈|彼得·叶茨]]、[[约翰·吉勒明|约翰·古勒米]]、[[罗纳德·尼姆|罗纳德·尼姆]]（{{lang|en|Ronald Neame}}）和[[山姆·畢京柏|萨姆·佩金帕]]都曾是电影的导演人选。[[马龙·白兰度|马龙·白兰度]]与[[吉恩·哈克曼|吉恩·哈克曼]]分别签约出演超人的父亲乔艾尔和反派[[莱克斯·卢瑟|莱克斯·卢瑟]]，[[盖·汉弥尔顿|盖·汉弥尔顿]]将出任导演。不过，白兰度当时在[[意大利|意大利]]因电影《[[巴黎最后的探戈|巴黎最后的探戈]]》而受到淫秽罪的指控，汉弥尔顿也因为纳税上的麻烦而不能到[[英格兰|英格兰]]参加拍摄<ref name="Dick">{{cite news| author = Daniel Dickholtz | title = Steel Dreams: Interview with Tom Mankiewicz | work = Starlog | date = 1998-12-16 | pages = 67–71}}</ref>。于是塞尔金德父子请来了[[理查德·唐纳|理查德·唐纳]]执导，唐纳则找来{{link-en|汤姆·曼凯维奇|Tom Mankiewicz}}为剧本润色，这也给剧本带来了浓烈的宗教色彩<ref name="believe">{{cite video | title = You Will Believe: The Cinematic Saga of Superman | format = DVD | publisher = Warner Bros. | year = 2006 | url = http://www.dvdtalk.com/reviews/25423/superman-ultimate-collectors-edition/ | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121203192554/http://www.dvdtalk.com/reviews/25423/superman-ultimate-collectors-edition/ | archivedate = 2012-12-03 | accessdate = 2014-08-27 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。

[[File:Clarksupescompare.jpg|thumb]]饰演超人和克拉克·肯特]]

[[克里斯托弗·里夫|克里斯托弗·里夫]]获选出演超人，不过最初塞尔金德父子对他并不如何看好<ref name="one on one" />。而白兰度虽然参加电影拍摄前连剧本也没有看过<ref name="believe" />，并且参与拍摄的时间一共也不到两个星期<ref name="one on one" />，更不用说出演的还是一个戏份很少的[[配角|配角]]，但他却得到了370万美元的片酬外加11.75%的票房利润分成<ref name="one on one" />。《超人》于1978年[[圣诞节|圣诞节]]档期上映，在商业和专业评论两方面都获得了成功<ref name="rotsup" /><ref name="supermanboxoffice" /><ref name="metacriticsuperman" />，不过电影的制片人认为，上映同期没有多少其它电影同台竞争是本片成功的一个重要因素<ref>''Pierre Spangler, Look up in the Sky! The Amazing Story of Superman.''</ref>。

=== 《超人II》（1980年） ===
{{Main|超人II}}
唐纳与塞尔金德父子关系欠佳，虽然有理查德·莱斯特从中调解<ref name="believe" />，但唐纳还是没有完成《超人II》。电影预算超支后，导演决定还是先暂停续集的拍摄，并且将其高潮戏段放到第一集中<ref name="one on one" /><ref name="believe" />。虽然《超人》上映后获得了很大的成功，但唐纳还是没有回来继续完成《超人II》<ref name="believe" />，这部电影是之后由莱斯特完成的，他也给了影片一个更为轻松的基调。塞尔金德父子还因财政上的原因而剪掉了白兰度出演的场景<ref name="one on one" />。之前为《超人》谱曲的[[约翰·威廉姆斯|约翰·威廉姆斯]]因为需要参加另外一部电影的作曲工作而退回了本片<ref name="one on one" />。《超人II》于1980年12月4日在[[澳大利亚|澳大利亚]]首映<ref name="Australia release">{{cite book | last = Langford | first = David | title = The Sex Column and Other Misprints | year = 2005 | publisher = Wildside Press | isbn = 978-1-930997-78-3 | page = 42 | accessdate = 2014-08-28 | url = http://books.google.com.hk/books?id=n78kYbvUd_8C&pg=PA42&redir_esc=y&hl=zh-CN&sourceid=cndr | archive-date = 2014-09-03 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140903050132/http://books.google.com.hk/books?id=n78kYbvUd_8C&pg=PA42&redir_esc=y&hl=zh-CN&sourceid=cndr | dead-url = no }}</ref>，1981年4月9日在[[英国|英国]]上映<ref>{{cite news | title = Entertainments (cinema listings) | author = | url = | newspaper = The Guardian | date = 1981-04-09}}</ref>，虽然面临《[[夺宝奇兵|夺宝奇兵]]》的强劲竞争，但仍然在商业和评论两方面都获得了成功<ref name="supermaniiboxoffice" /><ref name="rotsup2" /><ref name="metacriticsupermanii" />。2006年，理查德·唐纳应影迷之邀与制片人迈克尔·陶（{{lang|en|Michael Thau}}）合作推出了《超人2：理查德·唐纳剪辑版》，影片于2006年11月28日发行，获得了评论家和电影中几位演员的好评<ref name="rotsup2" />。

=== 《超人III》（1983年） ===
{{main|超人III}}
由伊利亚·塞尔金德所构思的第三部超人系列电影将故事的范围扩大到了[[宇宙|宇宙]]级别，并在其中引入了女超人以及两位[[超级坏蛋|超级坏蛋]]<ref name="believe" />。这个故事的特点是女超人与其中一位超级坏蛋的父女关系，以及超人和女超人之间的恋情，而根据漫画原著中的设定，这两位本应是表兄妹<ref>{{cite web | url = http://meatfighter.com/superman3/part4/s3_original_idea.pdf | format = [[PDF|PDF]] | title = STORY OUTLINE of SUPERMAN III | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140110160503/http://meatfighter.com/superman3/part4/s3_original_idea.pdf | publisher = Supermancinema.co.uk | accessdate = 2014-08-27 | archivedate = 2014-01-10 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。华纳兄弟公司没有接受这样的剧情设计，另外请人编写了《超人III》的剧本。[[理查德·普赖尔|理查德·普赖尔]]（{{lang|en|Richard Pryor}}）在片中扮演电脑高手格斯·戈尔曼（{{lang|en|Gus Gorman}}），他在一个百万富翁的操纵下制作出一种新的氪石，把超人转变成邪恶的另一个自我。改编后的剧本<ref name="believe" />把塞尔金德构思剧本中的一个超级坏蛋缩减成电影中邪恶的“终极电脑”<ref name="one on one" />。影片于1983年6月17日影片在美国上映，虽然票房上还算差强人意<ref name="supermaniiiboxoffice" />，但评价上却远远不及<ref name="rotsup3" /><ref name="metacriticsupermaniii" />，影片提名了两座[[金酸莓獎|金酸莓奖]]<ref name="worst">{{cite book | last = Wilson | first = John | title = The Official Razzie Movie Guide: Enjoying the Best of Hollywood's Worst | year = 2005 | publisher = Grand Central Publishing | isbn = 0-446-69334-0}}</ref>，特别是普赖尔的表演受到批评，认为前两部影片严肃的基调就毁在他的手里，此外对邪恶版超人的描绘也引起了争议。塞尔金德被拒绝的提案于2007年在网上发布<ref name="believe" />。

=== 《超人IV：寻求和平》（1987年） ===
{{main|超人IV：寻求和平}}
坎农影业接手了第4部超人电影的制作，克里斯托弗·里夫对这部电影所涉及的[[核武器|核武器]]主题很感兴趣，于是同意出演，这也成为里夫主演的超人系列电影中首部[[美国电影|美国电影]]（之前几部属[[英国电影|英国电影]]）<ref>{{cite web | url = http://explore.bfi.org.uk/4ce2b6bf3e269 | title = Superman II (1980) | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131031002952/http://explore.bfi.org.uk/4ce2b6bf3e269 | publisher = British Film Institute | accessdate = 2014-08-28 | archivedate = 2013-10-31 | deadurl = yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://explore.bfi.org.uk/4ce2b6958a07d | title = Superman III (1983) | publisher = British Film Institute | accessdate = 2014-08-28 | archivedate = 2014-05-26 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140526001544/http://explore.bfi.org.uk/4ce2b6958a07d }}</ref>。坎农决定将《超人IV》的预算从3500万美元大幅削减至1500万美元，这导致电影中所使用的特技效果很不理想，结合过于明显的剪辑痕迹，影片的反响是所有超人电影（不包括《女超人》）中最差的<ref name="believe" /><ref name="return">{{cite news | author = Adam Smith | title = All-American Hero | pages = 78–91 | publisher = Empire | date = 2006-05-26 | accessdate=2013-05-25}}</ref>，像《超人III》一样被提名两项金酸莓奖<ref name="worst" />。由于连续两部电影表现都很差，华纳兄弟公司决定暂时搁置这一系列<ref name="believe" />。

=== 衍生作品 ===
==== 《女超人》（1984） ====
{{Main|女超人 (電影)}}
塞尔金德父子在获得超人的电影版权期间，也取得了超人表妹“女超人”的电影版权<ref>{{cite news | title = Supergirl: She looks Super! Thanks for asking! | publisher = [[IGN|IGN]] | date = 2000-08-10 | url = http://uk.ign.com/articles/2000/08/10/supergirl | accessdate = 2014-08-27}}</ref>。1984年，里夫《超人》系列电影的[[衍生作品|衍生作品]]《女超人》正式上映，里夫原订会在片中[[友情客串|客串出镜]]，但最终还是没有实现<ref>''You Will Believe: The Cinematic Saga of Superman (Redemption)'', Warner Home Video, 2006.</ref>。{{link-en|海伦·斯雷特|Helen Slater}}出演女超人一角，这也是她出演的第一部电影<ref>{{cite news | author = Pantozzi, Jill | title = Helen Slater is Still "Super" | publisher = Comic Book Resources | date = 2009-12-07 | url = http://www.comicbookresources.com/?page=article&id=23956 | accessdate = 2014-08-27 | archivedate = 2013-12-02 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131202232048/http://www.comicbookresources.com/?page=article&id=23956 }}</ref>。不过虽然斯雷特是女主角，但片头出现的第一位演员姓名却是[[费·唐纳薇|费·唐纳薇]]，她在片中出演大反派塞琳娜（{{lang|en|Selena}}）。此外，马克·麦克卢尔（{{lang|en|Marc McClure}}）还回归出演了[[吉米·奥利森|吉米·奥利森]]（{{lang|en|Jimmy Olsen}}）一角<ref>{{cite web | title = Supergirl | publisher = British Film Institute | url = http://explore.bfi.org.uk/4ce2b6956508b | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140508030708/http://explore.bfi.org.uk/4ce2b6956508b | accessdate = 2014-08-27 | deadurl = yes | archivedate = 2014-05-08 }}</ref>。《女超人》票房和评价都惨不忍睹<ref name="supergirlboxoffice" /><ref name="rotgirl" />，比任何一部超人电影都要差<ref>{{cite news | author = Maslin, Janet | title = The Screen: Helen Slater as 'Supergirl' | work = [[纽约时报|The New York Times]] | date = 1984-11-22 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140123053544/http://www.nytimes.com/1984/11/22/movies/the-screen-helen-slater-as-supergirl.html | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nytimes.com/1984/11/22/movies/the-screen-helen-slater-as-supergirl.html | accessdate = 2014-08-27 | archivedate = 2014-01-23 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | author = Stecklow, Steve | title = Box Office Bombs May Turn Into Skyrockets On Videotape | work = [[芝加哥论坛报|Chicago Tribune]] | date = 1985-04-19 | url = http://articles.chicagotribune.com/1985-04-19/entertainment/8501230412_1_videotape-box-office-top-videocassette-rentals | accessdate = 2014-08-27 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140508042940/http://articles.chicagotribune.com/1985-04-19/entertainment/8501230412_1_videotape-box-office-top-videocassette-rentals | archivedate = 2014-05-08 | deadurl = no }}</ref>，不过斯雷特还是因该片获得了一项[[土星奖|土星奖]]提名<ref>{{cite news | title = Saturn Awards | date = 1985-02-22 | work = Times-News | location = Hendersonville, North Carolina | page = 11 | url = http://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=1665&dat=19850221&id=dmocAAAAIBAJ&sjid=x04EAAAAIBAJ&pg=6303,7066501 | accessdate = 2014-08-27 | archive-date = 2016-03-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160312084603/https://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=1665&dat=19850221&id=dmocAAAAIBAJ&sjid=x04EAAAAIBAJ&pg=6303,7066501 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

== 取消的电影项目 ==
《超人IV：寻求和平》上映后的17年时间里，华纳兄弟公司曾计划过多部超人系列电影的摄制，但其中大部分方案都在不同时期胎死腹中，这其间涉及了许多导演、编剧和演员，有些作品都已经进行实际拍摄阶段，前后花费了约5000万美元资金，但都没有任何作品面世。

=== 《超人V》 ===
《超人IV》上映前，坎农影业曾计划由[[艾伯特·潘|艾伯特·潘]]（{{lang|en|Albert Pyun}}）来执导这一系列的第5部电影，但《超人IV》的惨败导致坎农影业破产，超人系列的电影版权又回到了塞尔金德父子手中<ref name="White">{{cite news |author=Mike White |title=''Superman'': Grounded |work=Cahiers du cinéma |url=http://www.impossiblefunky.com/archives/issue_15/15_superman.asp?IshNum=15 |accessdate=2014-08-27 |archivedate=2012-06-27 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120627062338/http://www.impossiblefunky.com/archives/issue_15/15_superman.asp?IshNum=15 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。1990年代初，伊利亚·塞尔金德与电视剧《[[少年超人|少年超人]]》（{{lang|en|''Superboy''}}）的编剧[[卡里·贝茨|卡里·贝茨]]和马克·琼斯（{{lang|en|Mark Jones}}）一起编写了《超人{{lang|en|V}}》（{{lang|en|''Superman V''}}，又名《超人：新电影》，原名“{{lang|en|''Superman: The New Movie''}}”）的故事<ref name="one on one" />。故事中超人在缩小装进瓶子里的氪星首都坎多城死亡后又起死回生。巧合的是，{{lang|en|DC}}漫画之后于1992年出版的超人故事主线中也有其死亡后重生的类似情节。塞尔金德、贝茨和琼斯开发了两稿剧本，并打算请克里斯托弗·里夫回归出演超人<ref name="one on one" />。

=== 《超人重生》 ===
{{Quote box|width=40%|align=right|quote=“在任何一部好的超人电影里面，整个地球都必须处于重大的危险之中，里面必须有一个足够强大的恶棍，只有超人才能够阻止他。要想让电影变得刺激和精彩，这是唯一的办法。”|source=——《超人重生》的编剧乔纳森·勒姆金<ref name="corporate">{{cite book | author = David Hughes | title = The Greatest Sci-Fi Movies Never Made | url = https://archive.org/details/greatestscifimov0000hugh | year = 2001 | publisher = Independent Publishers Group | pages = [https://archive.org/details/greatestscifimov0000hugh/page/172 172]–186 | isbn = 1-55652-449-8}}</ref>}}

《超人之死》漫画的成功促使华纳兄弟公司于1993年初从塞尔金德父子手中买下了超人的电影版权，并将项目交给制片人{{link-en|乔恩·彼得斯|Jon Peters}}负责。公司不打算采用《超人：新电影》的剧本设定，于是彼得斯请乔纳森·勒姆金（{{lang|en|Jonathan Lemkin}}）来编写新的剧本。华纳兄弟公司要求新剧本要能够吸引主流观众，风格上可能获得20世纪90年代新生代电影观众的认同。此外还希望电影中增加一些适合与合家观赏的家庭电影元素，与《[[永远的蝙蝠侠|永远的蝙蝠侠]]》类似，这样有助于提高超人相关玩具产品的号召力，几家大型玩具厂商都要求要在2月中旬的[[美国国际玩具交易会|美国国际玩具交易会]]前看到勒姆金的剧本<ref name="corporate" />。

勒姆金创作的这个剧本题为《超人重生》，故事的主线是克拉克·肯特和路易斯·莱恩感情上的烦恼，以及超人与“末日”（{{lang|en|Doomsday}}）之间的大战。之后超人不敌末日，向路易丝表白后，他生命的力量也传导到了她的身上，路易丝神奇地产下一名男婴，这个孩子只用了3个星期就长到有21岁那么大，成为复活的新超人拯救了世界。华纳兄弟公司觉得《[[永远的蝙蝠侠|永远的蝙蝠侠]]》中也有着类似的主题结构，因此没有接受这个剧本<ref name="forever">{{cite book | author = Ken Hanke | title = Tim Burton: An Unauthorized Biography of the Filmmaker | year = 1999 | publisher = Renaissance Books | pages = 213–218 | isbn = 1-58063-162-2}}</ref>。

彼得斯于是又请来{{link-en|格雷戈里·波伊莱尔|Gregory Poirier}}改写剧本<ref name="corporate" />，波伊莱尔于1995年12月完成改写。这个故事同样涉及超人与路易斯·莱恩的感情问题，并且超人也同样为“末日”所杀。只是其复活后失去了一切超能力（或者准确地说是还没有学会如何使用自己的力量），因此穿上了一件可以模拟之前力量的机械战衣直至他恢复（学会使用）力量时止。根据剧本中的描述，这种力量从概念上与《[[星球大战|星球大战]]》中的[[原力|原力]]很相似。此外剧本中超人还有来自外星的盟友，另外还有其他多个反派角色出场<ref name="White" />。华纳兄弟公司对这个剧本很满意<ref name="forever" />，不过之后还是请了[[凯文·史密斯|凯文·史密斯]]来进行改写<ref name="Gross2">{{cite news | author = Edward Gross | title = ''SUPERMAN LIVES'', Part 2: Writer Kevin Smith | work = Mania Movies | url = http://www.mania.com/superman-lives-part-2-writer-kevin-smith_article_21118.html | date = 2000-05-12 | accessdate = 2014-08-27 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131021162929/http://www.mania.com/superman-lives-part-2-writer-kevin-smith_article_21118.html | archivedate = 2013-10-21 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。史密斯认为波伊莱尔的剧本对超人漫画原著缺乏足够的尊重，他之后在《与凯文·史密斯共度良宵》（{{lang|en|''An Evening with Kevin Smith''}}）中表示，这个剧本“就像超人电影的《蝙蝠侠》电视节目版本，非常不自然”<ref name="corporate" />。

=== 《超人的生活》 ===
{{main|超人复活夭折记}}
1996年8月，凯文·史密斯向彼得斯描述了自己的故事大纲，彼得斯同意让他编写剧本，但是提出了三个方面的要求。首先，超人需要穿上全黑色的套装<ref name="corporate" />，并且超人也不能飞<ref name="corporate" />。史密斯认为这样的话超人会“看起来像个严重超龄的童子军”<ref name="White" />，于是他描写超人飞行过程中会有“一个红蓝色的残影，并且每一次起飞时都会产生[[声爆|声爆]]”<ref name="boom!">{{cite news | author = Kevin Smith | title = Superman Lives Script | work = Script-O-Rama | date = 1997-03-27 | url = http://www.script-o-rama.com/movie_scripts/superman-lives-script.html | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140724132854/http://www.script-o-rama.com/movie_scripts/superman-lives-script.html | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2014-08-27 | archivedate = 2014-07-24 }}</ref>。彼得斯还希望电影的高潮戏段中超人与一个巨大的[[蜘蛛|蜘蛛]]作战。史密斯意识到自己只是来将一个已经成形的构思写成剧本，但还是接受了这些条件<ref name="corporate" />。彼得斯和华纳兄弟公司还让史密斯写了一个反派角色与[[北极熊|北极熊]]大战的情节，或是送给大反派莱克斯·卢瑟一只太空狗<ref name="Gross2" />。并且还因当时重新发行的《[[星球大战|星球大战]]》系列电影而在片中也加上了类似R2-D2，有情绪会思考的机器人角色<ref name="Gross2" />。彼得斯之后出任了1999年动作喜剧片《[[飙风战警|飙风战警]]》的制片人，并将其巨型蜘蛛的构想应用到了该片中<ref name="corporate" />。

史密斯所编写的《超人的生活》（{{lang|en|''Superman Lives''}}）剧本中有“末日”和“布莱恩尼阿克”（{{lang|en|Brainiac}}，直译有天才的意思）两个超级坏蛋角色，布莱恩尼阿克派出末日去杀死超人，并且因为知道超人需要通过阳光来获得力量而将[[太阳|太阳]]遮起来。布莱恩尼阿克还与莱克斯·卢瑟合作，而超人则经一个氪星的机器人复活，只是没有了超能力，这个机器人于是化身为一套战衣穿到了超人的身上来赋予他力量直到他恢复为止。布莱恩尼阿克试图夺得这个机器人并掌握其科技，但最终被超人打败<ref name="boom!"/>。史密斯所考虑的演员人选包括[[本·阿弗莱克|本·阿弗莱克]]饰演克拉克·肯特和超人，{{link-en|琳达·费奥伦蒂诺|Linda Fiorentino}}出演路易斯·莱恩，[[杰克·尼科尔森|杰克·尼科尔森]]饰演莱克斯·卢瑟，[[法米克·詹森|法米克·詹森]]诠释梅茜·格拉芙斯（{{lang|en|Mercy Graves}}），[[约翰·马奥尼|约翰·马奥尼]]饰演佩里·怀特（{{lang|en|Perry White}}），[[大卫·海德·皮尔斯|大卫·海德·皮尔斯]]（{{lang|en|David Hyde Pierce}}）扮演氪星机器人，[[杰森·李|杰森·李]]出演布莱恩尼阿克，另有杰森·缪斯（{{lang|en|Jason Mewes}}）诠释吉米·奥尔森<ref>{{cite news |title=Kevin Smith's ''Superman Lives'' cast |work=Superman Homepage |date=1999-03-02 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140309141256/http://www.supermanhomepage.com/news/1999-news/1999-news-movie.php?topic=1999-news-movie%2F0302 |url=http://www.supermanhomepage.com/news/1999-news/1999-news-movie.php?topic=1999-news-movie/0302 |accessdate=2014-08-27 |archivedate=2014-03-09 }}</ref>。

[[罗伯特·罗德里格兹|罗伯特·罗德里格兹]]获得了执导这部电影的邀请，他虽然很喜欢这个剧本，但由于已经承诺接拍青春恐怖片《[[老师不是人|老师不是人]]》而不得不推掉这次机会<ref name="corporate" />。史密斯原本建议请[[蒂姆·波顿|蒂姆·波顿]]来执导<ref name="Gross2" />，而且波顿也签下了500万美元的违约赔偿合同。华纳兄弟公司很快开始安排制作并将电影的上映时间定在1998年夏，以纪念超人一角在漫画杂志上出现60周年<ref name="forever" />。[[尼古拉斯·凯奇|尼古拉斯·凯奇]]是漫画杂志的粉丝，他同意出演并签订了2000万美元的违约赔偿合同，相信自由能够“重新构想这个角色”<ref name="corporate" />。彼得斯也觉得凯奇可以“让观众相信他（超人）真的是从外太空来的”<ref>{{cite book | author = Nancy Griffin, Kim Masters | title = Hit & Run: How Jon Peters and Peter Guber Took Sony For A Ride In Hollywood | year = 1997 | publisher = Simon & Schuster | page = 463 | isbn = 0-684-80931-1}}</ref>。波顿则表示由凯奇来出演将会“第一次让你真的相信没有人发现克拉克·肯特就是超人，他（凯奇）真的可以从物理上改变自己的人格形象”<ref name="effort">{{cite book | author = Mark Salisbury, Tim Burton | title = Burton on Burton: Revised Edition | url = https://archive.org/details/isbn_2900571229269 | year = 2006 | publisher = Faber and Faber | page = [https://archive.org/details/isbn_2900571229269/page/154 154] | isbn = 0-571-22926-3}}</ref>。[[凯文·斯派西|凯文·斯派西]]获邀出演莱克斯·卢瑟<ref name="effort" />，而[[蒂姆·艾伦|蒂姆·艾伦]]则表示已就出演大反派布莱恩尼阿克进行恰谈<ref name="bigpicture">{{cite news |author=Cindy Pearlman |title=Big Picture: ''Superman Lives'' |work=[[芝加哥太阳报|Chicago Sun-Times]] |date=1997-12-02 |archivedate=2008-03-29 |url=http://www.supermanhomepage.com/news/1997-news/1997-news-movie.php?topic=1997-news-movie/1202 |accessdate=2014-08-27 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080329142514/http://www.supermanhomepage.com/news/1997-news/1997-news-movie.php?topic=1997-news-movie%2F1202 |deadurl=no }}</ref>，不过[[吉姆·凯瑞|吉姆·凯瑞]]曾是这一角色的理想人选<ref name="Gross2" />。另有报道称[[柯特妮·考克斯|柯特妮·考克斯]]可能会出演路易斯·莱恩，史密斯则确认[[克里斯·洛克|克里斯·洛克]]将饰演吉米·奥尔森<ref name="bigpicture" />，[[迈克尔·基顿|迈克尔·基顿]]也确认自己将会出演，但表示其角色并不是蝙蝠侠<ref>{{cite news |title=Kevin Spacey and Courtney Cox in ''Superman Lives''? |work=Superman Homepage |date=1998-03-04 |archivedate=2014-01-05 |deadurl=no |url=http://www.supermanhomepage.com/news/1998-news/1998-news-movie.php?topic=1998-news-movie/0304 |accessdate=2014-08-27 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140105003628/http://www.supermanhomepage.com/news/1998-news/1998-news-movie.php?topic=1998-news-movie%2F0304 }}</ref>。电影的特效制作预计由[[工业光魔公司|工业光魔公司]]负责<ref name="corporate" />。

影片原定于1998年初开拍<ref>{{cite news | author = Anita M. Busch | url = http://variety.com/1997/scene/vpage/helmer-gilliam-readies-defective-loathing-1117434174/ | title = Helmer Gilliam readies 'Defective,' 'Loathing' | work = [[综艺_(杂志)|Variety]] | date = 1997-04-22 | accessdate = 2014-08-27 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140309160143/http://variety.com/1997/scene/vpage/helmer-gilliam-readies-defective-loathing-1117434174/ | archivedate = 2014-03-09 | deadurl = no }}</ref>，1997年6月，电影进入前期制作阶段<ref name="corporate" />，[[艺术指导|艺术指导]]瑞克·海因里希斯（{{lang|en|Rick Heinrichs}}）带领美术设计团队开始工作<ref name="effort" />。波顿决定请[[韦斯利·斯崔克|韦斯利·斯崔克]]（{{lang|en|Wesley Strick}}）改写史密斯的剧本，对此史密斯公开表示了自己的失望：“公司对我的作品很满意，然后蒂姆·波顿加入进来了。等到他签了违约赔偿合同后，他反过来说想要另拍一个自己的版本。所以你觉得华纳兄弟会支持哪一边？是就拍了部《[[疯狂店员|疯狂店员]]》（{{lang|en|''Clerks''}}）那个人，还是拍出来一部赚到5个亿的《蝙蝠侠》那个人？”<ref name="corporate" />斯崔克对史密斯剧本中超人失去超能力，然后需要依靠一个机器人的设定感到非常很不满<ref name="corporate" />。他还觉得剧情中大反派布莱恩尼阿克通过向太空发射一张圆盘来挡住太阳，以令需要阳光来获取能源的超人失去超能力这样的情节设定与《[[辛普森一家|辛普森一家]]》中一集的情节过于类似<ref name="corporate" />。不过在看过《超人之死与重生》（{{lang|en|''The Death and Return of Superman''}}）后，斯崔克也理解了史密斯的一些做法。斯崔克改写下的超人是一位[[存在主义|存在主义者]]，觉得对地球来说自己只是一个外人。超人受到布莱恩尼阿克和莱克斯·卢瑟的威胁，两个反派合并成为“莱克斯尼阿克”（{{lang|en|Lexiac}}），根据斯崔克的说法，这是“一个精神分裂/疯狂的超级大坏蛋”<ref name="corporate" />。超人被杀后在一种名叫“{{lang|en|K}}”的神力下复活，这种神力也是氪星的象征，然后他打败了莱克斯尼阿克<ref name="corporate" />。

美术设计师塞尔凡·德斯普里兹声称美术部门所需制作的东西与超人系列漫画小说几乎没有任何联系，并表示彼得斯“会带一些孩子过来，让他们对墙上的画作评分来评估玩具开发的可行性。这基本上就是一场玩具展！”<ref name="corporate" />彼得斯看到一期《[[国家地理_(杂志)|国家地理]]》杂志封面上有一张髑髅的照片，于是他找到了美术部门的工作人员，告知对方自己希望把片中大反派的太空船设计成同样的外形。波顿向德斯普里兹描述了布莱恩尼阿克的形象，德斯普里兹称那看起来就是“[[梅林_(亚瑟王传说)|梅林]]的头发，下面是个髑髅，上面扣个鱼缸”<ref name="corporate" />。概念画家洛尔夫·莫尔在一次接受采访时表示他设计了一套氪星机器人的外衣，这件道具计划用在一个该机器人变形为一部飞行器时使用<ref>{{cite news |title=Rolf Mohr Talks ''Superman Lives'' |work=Superman Homepage |date=2003-08-29 |archivedate=2011-08-26 |deadurl=yes |url=http://s323579992.onlinehome.us/news/2003-news/2003-news-movie.php?topic=2003-news-movie/0829i |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110826132153/http://s323579992.onlinehome.us/news/2003-news/2003-news-movie.php?topic=2003-news-movie%2F0829i |8= |accessdate=2011-08-26 }}</ref>。

{{Quote box|width=40%|align=left|quote=“我们拿到了凯文·史密斯的剧本，但他们又说根本不用去看，因为他们知道他（指史密斯）不会继续留在剧组中。所以我们以凯文·史密斯这个剧本为指引来了解一些大概需要做些什么的概念，并等待有新的剧本送来，但这个新剧本一直都没有出现。”| source=——美术设计师塞尔凡·德斯普里兹谈到《超人的生活》<ref name="corporate" />}}

波顿选择了[[宾夕法尼亚州|宾夕法尼亚州]]的[[匹兹堡|匹兹堡]]来作为电影中大都会的主要拍摄地点<ref name="corporate" />，而[[片场系统|片场系统]]也做了预留<ref name="corporate" />，但开拍日期却多次推迟<ref name="forever" />。开始建好的一小片氪星外景也因此销毁，凯奇甚至连服装都已经穿好了<ref>{{cite news |title=Sylvian Despretz Talks ''Superman Lives'' |work=Superman Homepage |date=2003-07-09 |url=http://www.supermanhomepage.com/news/2003-news/2003-news-movie.php?topic=2003-news-movie/0709i |accessdate=2014-08-27 |archivedate=2014-01-06 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140106040140/http://www.supermanhomepage.com/news/2003-news/2003-news-movie.php?topic=2003-news-movie%2F0709i }}</ref>。公司还曾考虑要把片名《超人的生活》改为《超人重生》<ref>{{cite news | url = http://variety.com/1997/film/news/at-play-in-the-fields-of-the-biz-1116680325/ | title = At play in the fields of the biz | work = [[综艺_(杂志)|Variety]] | date = 1997-12-16 | accessdate = 2014-08-27 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140106093830/http://variety.com/1997/film/news/at-play-in-the-fields-of-the-biz-1116680325/ | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2014-01-06 }}</ref>。此外，华纳兄弟公司觉得斯崔克的剧本拍摄成本太高，于是又请来[[丹·吉尔罗伊|丹·吉尔罗伊]]帮忙改写，来让其在经济上更为可行。吉尔罗伊将剧本从需要1.9亿美元预算降低到了1亿美元，然而由于其他电影项目和财政上的原因，公司还是不愿意直接开拍<ref>{{cite news |author=Michael Fleming |title=Dan Gilroy's Superman Script |work=[[综艺_(杂志)|Variety]] |date=1998-10-06 |pages=88–89 |accessdate=2014-08-27 |url=http://www.supermanhomepage.com/news/1998-news/1998-news-movie.php?topic=1998-news-movie/1006 |archivedate=2012-10-18 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121018035659/http://www.supermanhomepage.com/news/1998-news/1998-news-movie.php?topic=1998-news-movie%2F1006 |deadurl=no }}</ref>，而是让吉尔罗伊又创作了两稿剧本<ref name="Gross3">{{cite news | author = Edward Gross | title = ''SUPERMAN LIVES'', Part 3: Nicolas Cage | work = Mania Movies | url = http://www.mania.com/superman-lives-part-3-nicolas-cage_article_21288.html | date = 2000-05-19 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140106071309/http://www.mania.com/superman-lives-part-3-nicolas-cage_article_21288.html | accessdate = 2014-08-27 | archivedate = 2014-01-06 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。最终，华纳兄弟于1998年4月决定暂时不拍这部电影，波顿因此离开了剧组去拍摄《[[断头谷|断头谷]]》<ref name="forever" />。到了这个时候，项目已经花掉了3000万美元，但却也能取得任何实质性进展<ref name="corporate" />。波顿之后表示，参加《超人的生活》这一项目是他一生中最糟糕的经历，特别是与彼得斯和华纳在多个方面意见相左的情况下。“我基本上浪费了一整年。考虑到要和一些你很不希望合作的人一起工作，这真是一段很漫长的时间”<ref>{{cite book | author = Paul A. Woods | title = Tim Burton: A Child's Garden of Nightmares | url = https://archive.org/details/timburtonchildsg0000unse_x0j7 | year = 2007 | publisher = Plexus Publishing | page = [https://archive.org/details/timburtonchildsg0000unse_x0j7/page/150 150] | isbn = 0-85965-401-X}}</ref>。

出于对电影制作进展缓慢的失望，漫画小说的爱好者兼剧作家亚历克斯·福特（{{lang|en|Alex Ford}}）于1998年9月向华纳兄弟公司自荐了剧本《超人：钢铁之躯》，根据其设想，这将成为又一个总数达7部的大型系列电影。公司和彼得斯对福特的方案很有兴趣，不过之后双方还是因创作理念存在差异而未能继续合作<ref name="White" />。对于这次经历福特表示，“我可以肯定地告诉你他们对漫画缺乏了解。他们的目标观众并非你我这样花7美元去看电影的人，而是那些会花60美元购买玩具和餐盒的父母。这只是一笔生意，而且你觉得哪个更重要，是1.5亿的票房，还是6亿的商品成交额？”<ref name="Gross3" />

对吉尔罗伊的剧本，彼得斯先后联系过拉尔夫·仲达格（{{lang|en|Ralph Zondag}}）<ref name="corporate" />、[[迈克尔·贝|迈克尔·贝]]、[[谢加·凯普尔|谢加·凯普尔]]（{{lang|en|Shekhar Kapur}}）和[[马丁·坎贝尔|马丁·坎贝尔]]来执导，但他们都拒绝了<ref name="White" />，[[布莱特·拉特纳|布莱特·拉特纳]]也选择接拍《[[居家男人_(电影)|居家男人]]》而谢绝邀请<ref>{{cite news |title=Movie Preview December 15 |work=[[娱乐周刊|Entertainment Weekly]] |date=2000-08-11 |url=http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,87408,00.html |accessdate=2014-08-27 |archivedate=2014-03-09 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140309141242/http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0%2C%2C87408%2C00.html |deadurl=no }}</ref>，此外有报道称公司还考虑过请[[西蒙·韦斯特|西蒙·韦斯特]]或{{link-en|斯蒂芬·诺林顿|Stephen Norrington}}出任导演<ref>{{cite news |title=More Directing Choices for ''Superman'' Movie |work=Superman Homepage |date=1999-02-08 |url=http://www.supermanhomepage.com/news/1999-news/1999-news-movie.php?topic=1999-news-movie/0208 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140309124951/http://www.supermanhomepage.com/news/1999-news/1999-news-movie.php?topic=1999-news-movie%2F0208 |archivedate=2014-03-09 |deadurl=no |accessdate=2014-08-27 }}</ref>。1999年6月，小威廉·威谢尔（{{lang|en|William Wisher, Jr.}}）获聘撰写新的剧本，尼古拉斯·凯奇也在故事元素方面给予了协助<ref>{{cite news | author = Michael Fleming | url = http://variety.com/1999/film/news/wb-puts-superman-into-the-wisher-well-1117503619/ | title = WB puts ''Superman'' into the Wisher well | work = [[综艺_(杂志)|Variety]] | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140309155854/http://variety.com/1999/film/news/wb-puts-superman-into-the-wisher-well-1117503619/ | date = 1999-06-30 | accessdate = 2014-08-27 | archivedate = 2014-03-09 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。但到了2000年6月，凯奇也彻底退出了这个项目<ref>{{cite news | author = Lew Irwin | title = Nic Cage Gives Kryptonite To ''Superman Lives'' Movie | work = [[互联网电影数据库|Internet Movie Database]] | date = 2000-06-12 | url = http://www.imdb.com/news/wenn/2000-06-12#celeb1 | accessdate = 2014-08-27 | publisher = [[亚马逊公司|Amazon.com]] | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140324130835/http://www.imdb.com/news/wenn/2000-06-12#celeb1 | archivedate = 2014-03-24 }}</ref>，而威谢尔则于同年8月给出了新的剧本，报道称其中拥有一些类似于《[[黑客帝国|黑客帝国]]》的元素<ref name="White" />。2000年10月，漫画小说作者[[基思·吉芬|基思·吉芬]]（{{lang|en|Keith Giffen}}）设计了新的故事方案，不过华纳兄弟公司没有采纳<ref name="corporate" />，之后公司又联系了[[奥利弗·斯通|奥利弗·斯通]]担任导演，但也遭到了拒绝<ref name="White" />。2001年4月，公司花费170万美元薪酬请保罗·阿塔那斯奥（{{lang|en|Paul Attanasio}}）从零开始编写一个新剧本<ref name="corporate" />，彼得斯联系了[[威尔·史密斯|威尔·史密斯]]出演超人，但考虑到种族方面问题，对方同样予以谢绝<ref>{{cite news | author = Larry Carroll | url = http://www.mtv.com/news/1590297/will-smith-explains-why-nihilistic-self-destructive-hancock-suits-him-far-better-than-superman/ | title = Will Smith Explains Why Nihilistic, Self-Destructive Hancock Suits Him Far Better Than Superman | work = MTV News | date = 2008-07-02 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140827045032/http://www.mtv.com/news/1590297/will-smith-explains-why-nihilistic-self-destructive-hancock-suits-him-far-better-than-superman/ | archivedate = 2014-08-27 | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2014-08-27 }}</ref>。

=== 《蝙蝠侠对超人》（2000年代初） ===
2002年2月，[[J·J·艾布拉姆斯|J·J·艾布拉姆斯]]获聘编写一部新的超人题材电影剧本，其中将忽略《超人之死》的情节设计，以一个原创故事来重启这一系列<ref name="reboot">{{cite book | author = David Hughes | title = Comic Book Movies | isbn = 0-7535-0767-6 | publisher = Virgin Books | pages = 21–22 | year = 2003}}</ref>，最初定下的标题为《超人飞越》（{{lang|en|''Superman: Flyby''}}）<ref name="White" />。项目已经获得了拍摄许可，但导演[[约瑟夫·麦克金提·尼彻|约瑟夫·麦克金提·尼彻]]决定接拍《[[霹雳娇娃：全速进攻|霹雳娇娃：全速进攻]]》而放弃了计划<ref name="Stallville">{{cite news |author=Daniel Fierman; Nancy Miller; Brian M. Raftery |title=Stallville? |work=[[娱乐周刊|Entertainment Weekly]] |url=http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,432553~1~0~itsburdenitspain--its,00.html |date=2003-03-14 |accessdate=2014-08-27 |archivedate=2014-08-19 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140819144658/http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0%2C%2C432553~1~0~itsburdenitspain--its%2C00.html }}</ref>，公司于是联系了[[沃尔夫冈·彼德森|沃尔夫冈·彼德森]]来执导<ref name="Dynamic">{{cite news |author=Brian M. Raftery; Nancy Miller |title=Dynamic Duel |work=[[娱乐周刊|Entertainment Weekly]] |url=http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,321972~1~0~holyfranchiseinsidebatman,00.html |date=2002-07-09 |accessdate=2014-08-27 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140819141441/http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0%2C%2C321972~1~0~holyfranchiseinsidebatman%2C00.html |deadurl=no |archivedate=2014-08-19 }}</ref>。但到了2001年8月<ref>{{cite news | author = Brian Linder | title = More ''Batman'', ''Superman'' Insanity at WB | publisher = [[IGN|IGN]] | date = 2001-08-09 | url = http://www.ign.com/articles/2001/08/09/more-batman-superman-insanity-at-wb | accessdate = 2014-08-27 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131030213652/http://www.ign.com/articles/2001/08/09/more-batman-superman-insanity-at-wb | archivedate = 2013-10-30 | deadurl = no }}</ref>，[[安德鲁·凯文·沃克|安德鲁·凯文·沃克]]向华纳兄弟公司提出了《蝙蝠侠对超人》（{{lang|en|''Batman vs. Superman''}}）的构思，彼德森仍然担任导演，而艾布拉姆斯的剧本则暂时搁置<ref name="Dynamic" />。之后公司还请来了[[阿齐瓦·高斯曼|阿齐瓦·高斯曼]]改写沃克的剧本<ref name=" @#!*% ">{{cite book | author = David Hughes | title = Tales From Development  @#!*% | url = https://archive.org/details/talesfromdevelop00davi | isbn = 1-84023-691-4 | publisher = Titan Books | pages = [https://archive.org/details/talesfromdevelop00davi/page/205 205]–208 | year = 2003}}</ref>。

高斯曼改写的剧本于2002年6月21日完成，故事中蝙蝠侠布鲁斯·韦恩已经退休5年，[[阿尔弗莱德·潘尼沃斯|阿尔弗莱德·潘尼沃斯]]、[[詹姆斯·戈顿_(漫画)|詹姆斯·戈顿]]及[[迪克·格雷森|迪克·格雷森]]均已故世。与此同时，克拉克·肯特与路易斯·莱恩离婚后一直郁郁寡欢，布鲁斯与美丽的伊丽莎白·米勒成婚时，克拉克还是他的伴郎。然而两人度蜜月时，伊丽莎白被[[小丑_(漫画)|小丑]]所杀，布鲁斯因此不得不再次穿上蝙蝠侠战衣，他发现这一事件还牵涉到莱克斯·卢瑟于是寻求超人的帮助。但克拉克与拉娜·兰陷入了情网，因此拒绝了布鲁斯的请求。布鲁斯为此将伊丽莎白的惨死怪责在克拉克身上，两人于是变得敌对起来。不过当蝙蝠侠和超人发现这一切原来正是卢瑟的一个大阴谋时，他们决定联合起来阻止他<ref>{{cite news | author = Akiva Goldsman | title = ''Batman vs Superman'' 2nd Draft | work = Daily Scripts | url = http://www.dailyscript.com/scripts/asylum.pdf | date = 2002-06-21 | accessdate = 2014-08-27 | format = PDF | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20100107055225/http://www.dailyscript.com/scripts/asylum.pdf | archivedate = 2010-01-07 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。受到[[托比·马奎尔|托比·马奎尔]]在《[[蜘蛛侠_(电影)|蜘蛛侠]]》中表演的启发，彼得森打算寻找一个演员“既能真正表现出人物的复杂性和感情，又可以保持一个伟大超级英雄故事的趣味性”。据报道他为此考虑过[[马特·达蒙|马特·达蒙]]<ref name= @#!*% />、[[约翰尼·德普|约翰尼·德普]]、[[科林·法瑞尔|科林·法瑞尔]]、[[詹姆斯·弗兰科|詹姆斯·弗兰科]]、[[裘德·洛|裘德·洛]]和[[保罗·沃克|保罗·沃克]]来出演蝙蝠侠或超人<ref name="Dynamic" />。在克里斯托弗·诺兰执导的[[蝙蝠侠系列电影|三部蝙蝠侠电影]]中出演蝙蝠侠的[[克里斯蒂安·贝尔|克里斯蒂安·贝尔]]也曾获邀出演蝙蝠侠<ref>{{cite news | author = Smith, Adam | title = The Original American Psycho | work = Empire | date = 2005-7 | pages = 74–80, 82, 84, 87}}</ref>，而[[乔什·哈奈特|乔什·哈奈特]]则获邀扮演超人<ref name="Stallville" />。

电影于2003年初开拍，计划用5至6个月时间拍完并在2004年暑期上映<ref>{{cite news | author = Brian Linder | title = ''Batman vs. Superman'' in '04 | publisher = [[IGN|IGN]] | url = http://www.ign.com/articles/2002/07/09/batman-vs-superman-in-04 | date = 2002-07-09 | accessdate = 2014-08-27 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131030215319/http://www.ign.com/articles/2002/07/09/batman-vs-superman-in-04 | archivedate = 2013-10-30 }}</ref>。但在艾布拉姆斯提交了一份名为《超人飞越》的剧本后，华纳兄弟公司取消了这部电影的计划来考虑分别拍摄蝙蝠侠或超人题材的电影<ref name= @#!*% />。据彼得森所说，“阿兰·霍恩（华纳兄弟公司总裁）对此非常纠结，因为拍摄一部蝙蝠侠大战超人的电影这是个多么吸引人的概念啊”<ref>{{cite news | author = Brian Jacks | url = http://splashpage.mtv.com/2010/03/15/christian-bale-superman-wolfgang-petersen-batman-vs-superman/ | title = EXCLUSIVE: Christian Bale Met For Superman Role In Wolfgang Petersen's 'Batman Vs. Superman' | work = MTV News | date = 2010-03-15 | accessdate = 2014-08-27 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131203092314/http://splashpage.mtv.com/2010/03/15/christian-bale-superman-wolfgang-petersen-batman-vs-superman/ | archivedate = 2013-12-03 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。尽管项目就这样被取消了，但彼得森之后还是表示有兴趣执导《蝙蝠侠对超人》<ref>{{cite news | author = A.C. Ferrante | title = Profile: Wolfgang Peterson Reinvents ''Troy'' for DVD With New Director's Cut | publisher = If Magazine | date = 2007-09-18 | url = http://ifmagazine.com/feature.asp?article=2370 | accessdate = 2010-01-02 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20100102043432/http://ifmagazine.com/feature.asp?article=2370 | archivedate = 2010-01-02 }}</ref>，布莱恩·辛格也有同样的想法<ref>{{cite news | author = Clint Morris | title = Singer considering ''Batman Vs.Superman''? | publisher = Moviehole | date = 2006-07-07 | url = http://www.moviehole.net/news/20060707_singer_considering_batman_vssu.html | accessdate = 2008-06-10 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20080610031635/http://www.moviehole.net/news/20060707_singer_considering_batman_vssu.html | archivedate = 2008-06-10 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。在[[2007年电影|2007年电影]]《[[我是传奇|我是传奇]]》的片头，[[時報廣場|时代广场]]上有一条巨大的横幅上面显示着超人和蝙蝠侠的标志。这正是撰写了《蝙蝠侠对超人》和《我是传奇》剧本的阿齐瓦·高斯曼在片中所开的玩笑<ref>{{cite news | author = Larry Carroll | title = 'Batman Vs. Superman' Coming In 2009, But Will We Live To See It? | publisher = MTV Movies Blog | date = 2007-12-03 | url = http://moviesblog.mtv.com/2007/12/03/batman-vs-superman-coming-in-2009-but-will-we-live-to-see-it/ | accessdate = 2014-08-27 | archivedate = 2013-10-29 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131029210312/http://moviesblog.mtv.com/2007/12/03/batman-vs-superman-coming-in-2009-but-will-we-live-to-see-it/ }}</ref>。

=== 《超人飞越》 ===
2002年7月，{{lang|en|J·J}}·艾布拉姆斯完成了《超人飞越》的剧本。主要剧情为氪星上发生了一场内战，敌对的双方分别是超人的父亲乔艾尔和兄弟卡塔佐（{{lang|en|Kata-Zor}}），在被获胜的卡塔佐打入大牢前，乔艾尔将把儿子装进飞行器中朝地球发射过去来实现一个预言。乔纳森·肯特和玛莎·肯特收养了这个孩子并起名克拉克·肯特。克拉克长大后进入《行星日报》（{{lang|en|''Daily Planet''}}）社工作并爱上了路易斯·莱恩，不过路易斯此时更关心的是揭露莱克斯·卢瑟的阴谋。克拉克之后向全世界揭示自己就是超人，于是卡塔佐的儿子以及另外3名氪星人来到地球。超人寡不敌众被杀，到了氪星人的天堂后见到了在狱中自杀的父亲。然后超人复活过来回到地球打败了全部4名氪星人，剧本最终他前往氪星，为续集留下悬念<ref name="White" />。

2002年9月，华纳兄弟公司请布莱特·拉特纳来执导本片，起初还计划由一位名不见经传的演员来出演主角，于2003年下半年开拍<ref>{{cite news | author = Stax | title = Ratner Talks ''Superman'' | publisher = [[IGN|IGN]] | url = http://www.ign.com/articles/2002/09/17/ratner-talks-superman | date = 2002-09-17 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130421042508/http://www.ign.com/articles/2002/09/17/ratner-talks-superman | accessdate = 2014-08-27 | archivedate = 2013-04-21 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。拉特纳联系过乔什·哈奈特和裘德·洛来扮演超人，但他也承认，事实证明请一位大明星来饰演系列电影的主角是很困难的，因为其合约中都会要求保证出演续集。“没有哪位大明星会愿意签下这样的协议，但在向裘德和乔什介绍这部电影时，我也会警告他们接演超人可能导致的后果。可能今后10年他们都需要扮演这同一个角色，因为只要第一部电影能像大家期望的那样成功，我就会一连执导三部电影”<ref name="Hartnett">{{cite news | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130421042433/http://www.ign.com/articles/2003/01/31/ratner-bay-deny-superman-rumors | author = Stax | title = Ratner, Bay Deny ''Superman'' Rumors | work = IGN | url = http://www.ign.com/articles/2003/01/31/ratner-bay-deny-superman-rumors | date = 2003-01-31 | accessdate = 2014-08-27 | archivedate = 2013-04-21 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。哈奈特获得了以高达1亿美元片酬出演三部电影的合同，但他还是谢绝了<ref name="Singer">{{cite news | author = Michael Fleming; Cathy Dunkley | url = http://variety.com/2004/film/news/supe-s-on-with-x-man-1117907948/ | title = Supe's on with 'X' man | date = 2004-07-18 | work = [[综艺_(杂志)|Variety]] | accessdate = 2014-08-27 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140426202457/http://variety.com/2004/film/news/supe-s-on-with-x-man-1117907948/ | archivedate = 2014-04-26 }}</ref>。虽然《超人飞越》的预算超过了2亿美元（还不包括之前在《超人重生》、《超人的生活》和《蝙蝠侠对超人》中花掉的钱），但华纳兄弟公司仍然决定投拍，并将发行日期定在2004年暑期<ref name="Stallville" />。[[克里斯托弗·沃肯|克里斯托弗·沃肯]]有望出演佩里·怀特一角，拉特纳还表示有意请[[安东尼·霍普金斯|安东尼·霍普金斯]]扮演乔艾尔，[[拉尔夫·费恩斯|拉尔夫·费恩斯]]饰演莱克斯·卢瑟，这两位演员之前都曾出演过他执导的《[[红龙|红龙]]》<ref>{{cite news | author = Stax | title = Lex Lecter? Perry Walken? Jor-Ralph? | work = IGN | url = http://movies.ign.com/articles/390/390016p1.html | date = 2003-03-19 | accessdate = 2012-01-11 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120111172558/http://movies.ign.com/articles/390/390016p1.html | archivedate = 2012-01-11 | deadurl = yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=Brett Ratner Talks More on Superman |work=Superman Homepage |archivedate=2011-06-29 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110629142844/http://www.supermanhomepage.com/news/2002-news/2002-news-movie.php?topic=2002-news-movie%2F1021 |url=http://www.supermanhomepage.com/news/2002-news/2002-news-movie.php?topic=2002-news-movie/1021 |date=2002-10-21 |accessdate=2014-08-27 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

克里斯多夫·里夫是本片的项目顾问，他认为在《[[超人前传|超人前传]]》出演少年克拉克·肯特的[[汤姆·威灵|汤姆·威灵]]是一位理想人选。里夫还补充道，“（超人）这个角色比起扮演他的演员更重要，因为这是一个经久不衰的神话，所以肯定需要保持一定神秘感”<ref>{{cite news | author = Stax | title = Lara Lane? | work = IGN | url = http://www.ign.com/articles/2003/02/03/lara-lane | date = 2003-02-03 | accessdate = 2014-08-27 | archivedate = 2013-04-21 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130421042347/http://www.ign.com/articles/2003/02/03/lara-lane | deadurl = no }}</ref>。此外，[[保罗·沃克|保罗·沃克]]<ref name="White" />、[[阿什顿·库彻|阿什顿·库彻]]<ref name="Hartnett" />、[[布兰登·费舍|布兰登·费舍]]和[[马修·波莫|马修·波莫]]都曾是饰演超人的人选<ref name="Stallville" />，不过由于档期上与《[[70年代秀|70年代秀]]》和《超人的诅咒》存在冲突，并且也希望避免自己出演的角色过于雷同，库彻决定还是不出演这一角色<ref name="Kutcher">{{cite news | author = Stax | title = Kutcher Talks ''Superman'' | work = IGN | url = http://movies.ign.com/articles/389/389265p1.html | date = 2003-03-13 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120111172725/http://movies.ign.com/articles/389/389265p1.html | accessdate = 2012-01-11 | deadurl = yes | archivedate = 2012-01-11 }}</ref>。杰瑞·奥康奈尔曾表示有兴趣出演<ref name="Kutcher" />，[[大卫·伯伦纳兹|大卫·伯伦纳兹]]还参加了试镜，但之后因档期上与《[[夜行天使|夜行天使]]》存在冲突而退出<ref name="Boreanaz">{{cite news | author = Stax | title = Boreanaz, Webster Talk ''Superman'' | work = IGN | archivedate = 2012-01-11 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120111173007/http://movies.ign.com/articles/387/387939p1.html | url = http://movies.ign.com/articles/387/387939p1.html | date = 2003-03-04 | accessdate = 2012-01-11 }}</ref>。[[维克多·韦伯斯特|维克多·韦伯斯特]]已经分别试演过克拉克·肯特和超人<ref name="Boreanaz" />，[[詹姆斯·麦斯登|詹姆斯·麦斯登]]也与导演进行了会面<ref name="Boreanaz" /><ref>{{cite news | author = Kelvin Chavez | title = Marsden Talks Superman Returns! | publisher = Latino Review | url = http://www.latinoreview.com/news/marsden-talks-superman-returns-557 | date = 2006-05-12 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120113045734/http://www.latinoreview.com/news/marsden-talks-superman-returns-557 | accessdate = 2012-01-13 | deadurl = yes | archivedate = 2012-01-13 }}</ref>。之前拒绝参加超人一角试镜的[[乔尔·埃哲顿|乔尔·埃哲顿]]（{{lang|en|Joel Edgerton}}）参加了反派角色泰佐尔的试镜，不过到了2003年3月，由于演员选择方面的困难以及与乔恩·彼得斯之间出现的暴力分歧<ref>{{cite news | author = Lew Irwin | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121107120559/http://www.imdb.com/news/wenn/2003-03-10#celeb1 | url = http://imdb.com/news/wenn/2003-03-10#celeb1 | title = ''Superman'' Makers in Angry Feud | work = [[互联网电影数据库|Internet Movie Database]] | date = 2003-03-10 | accessdate = 2014-08-27 | publisher = [[亚马逊公司|Amazon.com]] | archivedate = 2012-11-07 }}</ref>，导演布莱特·拉特纳退出了剧组<ref>{{cite news | author = Stax | title = Ratner off ''Superman'' | work = IGN | url = http://movies.ign.com/articles/390/390115p1.html | date = 2003-03-20 | accessdate = 2012-01-11 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120111173115/http://movies.ign.com/articles/390/390115p1.html | archivedate = 2012-01-11 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。

导演退出后，约瑟夫·麦克金提·尼彻回归接手，费舍虽然有兴趣，但也担心角色雷同的问题<ref>{{cite news | author = Stax | title = Fraser Talks ''Superman'' | publisher = [[IGN|IGN]] | url = http://www.ign.com/articles/2003/11/03/fraser-talks-superman | date = 2003-11-03 | accessdate = 2014-08-27 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130421042332/http://www.ign.com/articles/2003/11/03/fraser-talks-superman | archivedate = 2013-04-21 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。[[塞尔玛·布莱尔|塞尔玛·布莱尔]]就出演路易斯·莱恩一角开始谈判<ref>{{cite news | author = Stax | title = ''Superman'' Taking Baby Steps? | work = [[IGN|IGN]] | url = http://www.ign.com/articles/2004/01/14/superman-taking-baby-steps | date = 2004-01-14 | accessdate = 2014-08-27 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130421042302/http://www.ign.com/articles/2004/01/14/superman-taking-baby-steps | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2013-04-21 }}</ref>，此外{{lang|en|ESC}}娱乐公司获聘负责电影的视觉特技效果制作，[[斯坦·温斯顿|斯坦·温斯顿]]将会制作片中的一些模型，金·莱布勒里（{{lang|en|Kim Libreri}}）担任电影特效总监<ref>{{cite news | author = Stax | title = ''Superman'' Hirings | publisher = [[IGN|IGN]] | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130421042424/http://www.ign.com/articles/2004/05/24/superman-hirings | archivedate = 2013-04-21 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.ign.com/articles/2004/05/24/superman-hirings | date = 2004-03-24 | accessdate = 2014-08-27 }}</ref>。尼彻联系了[[希亚·拉博夫|希亚·拉博夫]]来出演吉米·奥尔森，并打算找个无名小卒扮演超人。[[斯嘉丽·约翰逊|斯嘉丽·约翰逊]]将出演路易斯·莱恩，而[[约翰尼·德普|约翰尼·德普]]则会扮演莱克斯·卢瑟<ref>{{cite news | author = William Keck | title = ''I, Robot'' Has Superstar Input | work = [[USA_Today|USA Today]] | url = http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/people/2004-07-08-irobot-premiere_x.htm | date = 2004-07-08 | accessdate = 2014-08-27 | archivedate = 2013-08-28 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130828104649/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/people/2004-07-08-irobot-premiere_x.htm }}</ref>。不过尼彻在2012年接受采访时表示，[[小罗伯特·唐尼|小罗伯特·唐尼]]已入选出演莱克斯·卢瑟<ref name="playlist">{{cite news | author = Gabe Toro | url = http://blogs.indiewire.com/theplaylist/022012/mcg-says-robert-downey-jr-wouldve-been-lex-luthor-in-his-superman-describes-his-original-darker-ending-for-terminator-salvation?utm_source=dlvr.it&utm_medium=twitter | title = McG Says Robert Downey Jr. Would've Been Lex Luthor In His 'Superman'; Describes His Original, Darker Ending For 'Terminator: Salvation' | publisher = Indiewire | date = 2012-02-20 | accessdate = 2014-08-27 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140413180734/http://blogs.indiewire.com/theplaylist/022012/mcg-says-robert-downey-jr-wouldve-been-lex-luthor-in-his-superman-describes-his-original-darker-ending-for-terminator-salvation?utm_source=dlvr.it&utm_medium=twitter | archivedate = 2014-04-13 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。尼尔·{{lang|en|H}}·莫瑞兹（{{lang|en|Neal H. Moritz}}）和吉尔伯特·阿德勒（{{lang|en|Gilbert Adler}}）计划出任电影的[[制片人|制片人]]。尼彻还委托乔什·施瓦兹改写艾布拉姆斯的剧本。华纳兄弟公司原计划安排本片在澳大利亚拍摄，但尼彻希望改为在加拿大拍摄，这会导致拍摄成本高出2500万美元。尼彻还拍摄了多位演员的样本片段，如[[杰森·贝尔|杰森·贝尔]]（{{lang|en|Jason Behr}}）、[[亨利·卡维尔|亨利·卡维尔]]、[[贾德·帕达里克|贾德·帕达里克]]<ref name="Singer" />和[[迈克尔·卡西迪|迈克尔·卡西迪]]<ref>{{cite news | author = Oscar Dahl | title = Exclusive Interview: Michael Cassidy, from Hidden Palms Input | work = BuddyTV | url = http://www.buddytv.com/articles/hidden-palms/exclusive-interview-michael-ca-7511.aspx | date = 2007-06-20 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130517051113/http://www.buddytv.com/articles/hidden-palms/exclusive-interview-michael-ca-7511.aspx | archivedate = 2013-05-17 | deadurl = yes | accessdate = 2014-08-27 | df =  }}</ref>。不过最终由于预算方面的问题和拍摄地点上与华纳兄弟公司无法达成一致，尼彻也退出了剧组。他认为“在另一片大陆上拍摄美国的心脏地带是不恰当的”，并因此选择在[[纽约|纽约]]和加拿大进行拍摄，但华纳兄弟公司则希望在[[澳大利亚|澳大利亚]]的[[悉尼|悉尼]]进行<ref>{{cite news | author = Gabe Toro | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140413180734/http://blogs.indiewire.com/theplaylist/022012/mcg-says-robert-downey-jr-wouldve-been-lex-luthor-in-his-superman-describes-his-original-darker-ending-for-terminator-salvation?utm_source=dlvr.it&utm_medium=twitter | archivedate = 2014-04-13 | deadurl = yes | url = http://blogs.indiewire.com/theplaylist/022012/mcg-says-robert-downey-jr-wouldve-been-lex-luthor-in-his-superman-describes-his-original-darker-ending-for-terminator-salvation?utm_source=dlvr.it&utm_medium=twitter | title = McG Says Robert Downey Jr. Would've Been Lex Luthor In His 'Superman'; Describes His Original, Darker Ending For 'Terminator: Salvation' | publisher = Indiewire | date = 2012-02-20 | accessdate = 2014-08-27 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | author = Lew Irwin | url = http://imdb.com/news/sb/2004-07-12#film4 | title = McG Out As Director of ''Superman'' Sequel | work = [[互联网电影数据库|Internet Movie Database]] | date = 2004-07-12 | accessdate = 2012-11-07 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121107120605/http://www.imdb.com/news/sb/2004-07-12#film4 | archivedate = 2012-11-07 | publisher = [[亚马逊公司|Amazon.com]] }}</ref>。之后这位导演承认自己其实是有飞行恐惧症所以不愿意去澳大利亚<ref name="playlist" /><ref>{{cite news | author = Lew Irwin | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121107120611/http://www.imdb.com/news/wenn/2005-10-19#celeb9 | url = http://www.imdb.com/news/wenn/2005-10-19#celeb9 | title = Moviemaker McG's Fear of Flying Cost Him ''Superman'' | work = [[互联网电影数据库|Internet Movie Database]] | date = 2005-10-19 | accessdate = 2013-05-25 | archivedate = 2012-11-07 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。尼彻退出后，艾布拉姆斯希望可以亲自执导自己的剧本<ref>{{cite news | author = Michael Fleming; Dave McNary | url = http://variety.com/2004/film/news/par-girding-up-for-war-1117908978/ | title = Par girding up for 'War' | work = [[综艺_(杂志)|Variety]] | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130604150328/http://variety.com/2004/film/news/par-girding-up-for-war-1117908978/ | date = 2004-08-11 | accessdate = 2014-08-27 | archivedate = 2013-06-04 | deadurl = no }}</ref>，但华纳兄弟公司于2004年7月选择了[[布莱恩·辛格|布莱恩·辛格]]，他之后导演并推出了《超人归来》<ref>{{cite news | author = Stax | title = ''Superman'' Director Up, Up, and Away! | publisher = [[IGN|IGN]] | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130421042440/http://www.ign.com/articles/2004/07/12/superman-director-up-up-and-away | archivedate = 2013-04-21 | url = http://www.ign.com/articles/2004/07/12/superman-director-up-up-and-away | date = 2004-07-11 | accessdate = 2014-08-27 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。

== 《超人归来》（2006年） ==
[[File:Brandon_Routh_by_Gage_Skidmore.jpg|right]]》中饰演超人]]
{{Main|超人归来}}
布莱恩·辛格从儿时起就是理查德·唐纳执导《超人》的粉丝，所以华纳兄弟公司虽然是在拉特纳和尼彻都退出后再请他来执导《超人归来》，但他还是马上就接受了，并且放弃了另外两部已经进入前期制作的电影《[[X战警3：背水一战|X战警3：背水一战]]》（该片因此改由拉特纳执导）和[[1976年电影|1976年电影]]《[[我不能死|我不能死]]》（{{lang|en|''Logan's Run''}}）的重拍片。《超人归来》从情节设定上相当于《超人》和《超人II》的续集<ref name="ct">{{cite news | author = Peter T. Chattaway | url = http://www.christianitytoday.com/ct/2006/juneweb-only/supermanreturns.html | title = Superman Returns | work = Christianity Today | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121014172653/http://www.christianitytoday.com/ct/2006/juneweb-only/supermanreturns.html | date = 2006-06-28 | accessdate = 2014-08-27 | archivedate = 2012-10-14 | deadurl = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | author = Manohla Dargis | url = http://movies.nytimes.com/2006/06/27/movies/27supe.html | title = 'Superman Returns' to Save Mankind From Its Sins | work = [[纽约时报|The New York Times]] | date = 2006-06-27 | accessdate = 2013-05-25 | publisher = The New York Times Company | archivedate = 2013-06-22 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130622023820/http://movies.nytimes.com/2006/06/27/movies/27supe.html }}</ref>，没有考虑《超人III》和《超人IV：寻求和平》的内容<ref name="ct"/>。辛格执导的这个故事讲述超人前往氪星历时5年来寻找幸存者，回到地球后却发现挚爱的路易斯·莱恩已经订婚，而且已经有了孩子。辛格还仿照唐纳的做法选择了与当年克里斯多夫·里夫一样毫无名气的[[布兰登·罗斯|布兰登·罗斯]]来扮演超人，这位演员的外型还和里夫有些相似。出演配角的则都是更为大牌的演员，如扮演莱克斯·卢瑟的[[凯文·斯派西|凯文·斯派西]]等。辛格还将他之前拍摄《[[X战警2|X战警2]]》的整个剧组都一起请来再在这部电影中合作，并且通过利用以前电影拍摄的胶片让马龙·白兰度也出现在本片中。《超人归来》上映后获得了不错的评价，全球票房收入约为3.91亿美元。

=== 续集提案 ===
2006年2月，华纳兄弟公司宣布将于2009年为该片推出一部续集，导演仍然是布莱恩·辛格，这时距《超人归来》发行还有四个月<ref>{{cite news | title = Studio Sets ''Super'' Sequels | work = IGN | date = 2006-02-23 | url = http://www.ign.com/articles/2006/02/23/studio-sets-super-sequels | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140219212929/http://www.ign.com/articles/2006/02/23/studio-sets-super-sequels | accessdate = 2014-08-27 | archivedate = 2014-02-19 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。布兰登·罗斯<ref name="update">{{cite news |author=Kellvin Chavez |title=Exclusive: DC Comics President Gives ''Superman'' Update |url=http://www.latinoreview.com/news/exclusive-dc-comics-president-gives-superman-update-5511 |work=Latino Review |date=2008-10-09 |accessdate=2013-05-27 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081011054438/http://www.latinoreview.com/news/exclusive-dc-comics-president-gives-superman-update-5511 |archivedate=2008-10-11 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>、[[凯特·波茨沃斯|凯特·波茨沃斯]]<ref>{{cite news | author = Heather Newgen | title = Superman Returns' Lois Lane, Kate Bosworth | publisher = Superhero Hype! | date = 2006-06-16 | url = http://www.superherohype.com/features/91245-superman-returns-lois-lane-kate-bosworth | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140827083208/http://www.superherohype.com/features/91245-superman-returns-lois-lane-kate-bosworth | archivedate = 2014-08-27 | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2014-08-27 }}</ref>、凯文·斯派西<ref>{{cite news | author = Anne Thompson | title = Spacey set for ''Superman'' sequel | publisher = ''Variety'' | date = 2007-07-10 | archivedate = 2013-07-20 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130720080628/http://variety.com/2007/film/news/spacey-set-for-superman-sequel-2-1117968333/ | deadurl = no | url = http://variety.com/2007/film/news/spacey-set-for-superman-sequel-2-1117968333/ | accessdate = 2014-08-27 }}</ref>、[[萨姆·亨廷顿|萨姆·亨廷顿]]（{{lang|en|Sam Huntington}}）<ref>{{cite news | author = Heather Newgen | title = Huntington Signed for Two ''Superman'' Sequels | publisher = Superhero Hype! | date = 2006-06-09 | url = http://www.superherohype.com/features/91225-huntington-signed-for-two-superman-sequels | accessdate = 2014-08-27 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140827083436/http://www.superherohype.com/features/91225-huntington-signed-for-two-superman-sequels | archivedate = 2014-08-27 | deadurl = no }}</ref>、[[弗兰克·兰格拉|弗兰克·兰格拉]]<ref>{{cite news | author = Edward Douglas | title = Frank Langella on the Return of Perry White | publisher = Superhero Hype! | date = 2007-11-08 | url = http://www.superherohype.com/features/95247-frank-langella-on-the-return-of-perry-white | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140827083556/http://www.superherohype.com/features/95247-frank-langella-on-the-return-of-perry-white | accessdate = 2014-08-27 | archivedate = 2014-08-27 | deadurl = no }}</ref>和特里斯坦·雷克·勒布（{{lang|en|Tristan Lake Leabu}}）都将继续出演同一角色<ref name="brain">{{cite news | author = Fred Topel | title = Brandon Routh and Bryan Singer Tease ''Superman Returns'' Sequel | publisher = Flixster | work = [[烂番茄|Rotten Tomatoes]] | date = 2006-11-17 | url = http://www.rottentomatoes.com/news/1647830/brandon_routh_and_bryan_singer_tease_quotsuperman_returnsquot_sequel/ | accessdate = 2014-08-27 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140827083855/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/news/1647830/brandon_routh_and_bryan_singer_tease_quotsuperman_returnsquot_sequel/ | archivedate = 2014-08-27 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。为此辛格放弃了执导《我不能死》重拍片和有关[[哈维·米尔克|哈维·米尔克]]题材小说改编电影的机会<ref>{{cite news | author = Michael Fleming; Pamela McClintock | title = Inside Move: ''Superman'' playing with Singer's sked | publisher = Variety | date = 2006-05-15 | url = http://variety.com/2006/film/news/inside-move-superman-playing-with-singer-s-sked-1200336420/ | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140827084051/http://variety.com/2006/film/news/inside-move-superman-playing-with-singer-s-sked-1200336420/ | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2014-08-27 | accessdate = 2014-08-27 }}</ref>。编剧迈克尔·道赫蒂（{{lang|en|Michael Dougherty}}）打算让续集成为一部“动作集锦”，并写入“其他氪星人”<ref>{{cite news | author = Clint Morris | url = http://moviehole.net/201033129-what-would-doughertys-superman-sequel-have-been | title = What would Dougherty's Superman sequel have been? | work = Moviehole | date = 2010-11-05 | accessdate = 2014-08-27 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130630070033/http://moviehole.net/201033129-what-would-doughertys-superman-sequel-have-been | archivedate = 2013-06-30 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>和反派角色<ref>{{cite news | author = Frosty | title = Bryan Singer – Exclusive Video Interviews at the 2007 Saturn Awards | publisher = Collider.com | date = 2007-05-11 | url = http://collider.com/movie/article.asp/aid/4346/tcid/1 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140827084750/http://collider.com/movie/article.asp/aid/4346/tcid/1 | accessdate = 2014-08-27 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2014-08-27 }}</ref>，甚至包括像[[比扎罗|比扎罗]]（{{lang|en|Bizarro}}）这样拥有几乎所有超人力量的恶魔<ref name="brain" />。《超人归来》片尾在太空中漂浮的氪星陆块将成为推动续集剧情发展的重要元素<ref name="sequel/DVD">{{cite news | author = Scott Chitwood | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140827084946/http://www.superherohype.com/features/91545-exclusive-singer-on-superman-sequel-dvd | title = Exclusive: Singer on ''Superman'' Sequel & DVD | publisher = Superhero Hype! | date = 2006-07-22 | archivedate = 2014-08-27 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.superherohype.com/features/91545-exclusive-singer-on-superman-sequel-dvd | accessdate = 2014-08-27 }}</ref>。虽然《超人归来》所获评价以正面为主，但其票房表现却令华纳兄弟公司和[[传奇电影公司|传奇电影公司]]感到有些失望<ref name="variety.com">{{cite news | author = Pamela McClintock | title = WB mulls ''Superman'' redux | publisher = Variety | date = 2006-08-13 | url = http://variety.com/2006/more/news/wb-mulls-superman-redux-1200342128/ | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140827085127/http://variety.com/2006/film/news/wb-mulls-superman-redux-1200342128/ | accessdate = 2014-08-27 | archivedate = 2014-08-27 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。华纳兄弟总裁阿兰·{{lang|en|F}}·霍恩（{{lang|en|Alan F. Horn}}）对此表示，《超人归来》的确是一部很成功的电影，但是它本“应该在全世界拿下5个亿的票房。或许我们应该在其中加入更多的动作戏码来满足年轻的男性观众”<ref>{{cite news | title = Horn Planning ''Superman'' Sequel for 2009 | publisher = Superhero Hype! | date = 2006-08-18 | url = http://www.superherohype.com/features/91753-horn-planning-superman-sequel-for-2009 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140827085347/http://www.superherohype.com/features/91753-horn-planning-superman-sequel-for-2009 | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2014-08-27 | archivedate = 2014-08-27 }}</ref>。对于公司的抱怨，辛格觉得简直难以置信，他说：“这电影卖了4个亿！我真不明白这年代里他们到底还想怎么样才不算业绩欠佳”<ref name=singer-talks>{{cite news | author = Olly Richards | title = Singer Talks ''Superman Returns'' Sequel | publisher = ''Empire'' | date = 2008-03-12 | url = http://www.empireonline.com/news/story.asp?NID=22165 | accessdate = 2014-08-27 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140701171453/http://www.empireonline.com/news/story.asp?NID=22165 | archivedate = 2014-07-01 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。《超人归来》的所有开支一共达到2.09亿美元，但华纳兄弟公司最高只打算为续集投资1.75亿美元<ref>{{cite news | author = Stephen Galloway | title = Studios are hunting the next big property | work = [[好莱坞报道|The Hollywood Reporter]] | date = 2007-07-10 | archivedate = 2014-03-15 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140315045525/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/studios-are-hunting-next-big-142448 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/studios-are-hunting-next-big-142448 | accessdate = 2014-08-27 }}</ref><ref name="Pam">{{cite news | author = Pamela McClintock | title = Singer's zinger: another 'Superman' | work = [[综艺_(杂志)|Variety]] | date = 2006-10-30 | archivedate = 2013-12-18 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131218085901/http://variety.com/2006/film/news/singer-s-zinger-another-superman-1117952909/ | deadurl = no | url = http://variety.com/2006/film/news/singer-s-zinger-another-superman-1117952909/ | accessdate = 2014-08-27 }}</ref>。

《超人归来》续集的拍摄原定于2007年中期展开<ref>{{cite news | author = Michael Tsai | title = Sequel to ''Superman Returns'' due in 2009 | work = The Honolulu Advertiser | date = 2006-11-08 | url = http://the.honoluluadvertiser.com/article/2006/Nov/08/br/br0948627351.html | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140101091515/http://the.honoluluadvertiser.com/article/2006/Nov/08/br/br0948627351.html | accessdate = 2014-08-27 | archivedate = 2014-01-01 | dead-url = no }}</ref>，但辛格决定接拍《[[行动目标希特勒|行动目标希特勒]]》<ref>{{cite news | author = Michael Fleming | title = United Artists grabs Singer thriller | publisher = ''Variety'' | date = 2007-03-13 | url = http://variety.com/2007/film/news/united-artists-grabs-singer-thriller-1117961116/ | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140827085925/http://variety.com/2007/film/news/united-artists-grabs-singer-thriller-1117961116/ | accessdate = 2014-08-27 | archivedate = 2014-08-27 | deadurl = no }}</ref>，于是拍摄就推迟到了2008年3月<ref>{{cite news | title = ''Superman'' Sequel Eyeing March '08 Start | publisher = Superhero Hype! | date = 2007-03-19 | url = http://www.superherohype.com/features/93079-superman-sequel-eyeing-march-08-start | accessdate = 2014-08-27 | archivedate = 2014-08-27 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140827090028/http://www.superherohype.com/features/93079-superman-sequel-eyeing-march-08-start }}</ref>，可编剧道赫蒂和[[丹·哈里斯|丹·哈里斯]]（{{lang|en|Dan Harris}}）又决定退出参与其它项目<ref>{{cite news | author = Marc Graser | title = ''Superman'' writers won't return | publisher = ''Variety'' | date = 2007-10-21 | url = http://variety.com/2007/film/news/superman-writers-won-t-return-1117974449/ | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140827090237/http://variety.com/2007/film/news/superman-writers-won-t-return-1117974449/ | accessdate = 2014-08-27 | archivedate = 2014-08-27 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。2007年11月5日开始直至2008年2月12日才结束的[[2007年－2008年美国编剧协会大罢工|2007年－2008年美国编剧协会大罢工]]则令影片的发行时间推迟到了2010年<ref>{{cite news | author = Stax | title = ''JLA'' Deadline Looms | publisher = [[IGN|IGN]] | date = 2008-01-14 | url = http://www.ign.com/articles/2008/01/14/jla-deadline-looms | accessdate = 2014-08-27 | archivedate = 2014-02-19 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140219170939/http://www.ign.com/articles/2008/01/14/jla-deadline-looms }}</ref>。辛格在2008年3月时仍然把这部续集视为首要目标，并表示影片正在进行前期开发<ref name="singer-talks" />，布兰登·罗斯则预期电影将在2009年初开拍<ref>{{cite news | author = Frosty | title = Brandon Routh Exclusive Video Interview - ''Lie to Me'' | url = http://collider.com/movie/article.asp/aid/7675/tcid/1 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140827090502/http://collider.com/movie/article.asp/aid/7675/tcid/1 | publisher = Collider.com | date = 2008-04-23 | accessdate = 2014-08-27 | archivedate = 2014-08-27 }}</ref>。{{lang|en|DC}}漫画总裁[[保罗·里维兹|保罗·里维兹]]（{{lang|en|Paul Levitz}}）也希望罗斯可以像《超人归来》中那样继续出演超人<ref name="update" />，但是公司与其签订的合约将于2009年到期，因此电影需要尽快开拍<ref>{{cite news | author = Josh Wigler | title = Brandon Routh Says His 'Superman' Contract Has Expired | url = http://splashpage.mtv.com/2009/07/06/brandon-routh-says-his-superman-contract-has-expired/ | work = MTV News | date = 2009-08-14 | accessdate = 2014-08-27 | archivedate = 2014-01-01 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140101135603/http://splashpage.mtv.com/2009/07/06/brandon-routh-says-his-superman-contract-has-expired/ | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。但是，由于华纳兄弟公司决定重启超人系列电影，辛格退出了本片的摄制计划，接拍《[[巨人捕手杰克|巨人捕手杰克]]》和《[[太空堡垒卡拉狄加|太空堡垒卡拉狄加]]》的改编电影<ref>{{cite news | author = Borys Kit | url = http://www.backstage.com/news/bryan-singer-to-direct-battlestar-film/ | title = Bryan Singer to direct 'Battlestar' film | work = [[好莱坞报道|The Hollywood Reporter]] | date = 2009-08-13 | accessdate = 2014-08-27 | archivedate = 2014-08-27 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140827090841/http://www.backstage.com/news/bryan-singer-to-direct-battlestar-film/ | deadurl = no }}</ref>。华纳兄弟公司制片总监杰夫·罗宾诺夫曾于2008年8月表示，《超人归来》在人物刻划等多个方面与其预想的并不一致，导致续集也未能像一开始所计划的那样在2009年圣诞节档期上映<ref name="wall">{{cite news |first=Lauren A. E. |last=Schuker |title=Warner Bets on Fewer, Bigger Movies |work=The Wall Street Journal |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5xLzZSe7O?url=http://online.wsj.com/article/SB121936107614461929.html |date=2008-08-22 |deadurl=no |url=http://online.wsj.com/article/SB121936107614461929.html |accessdate=2013-10-04 |archivedate=2011-03-21 }}. .</ref>。

