=== 《超人：钢铁之躯》（2013年） ===
[[File:Henry_Cavill_SDCC_2014_(cropped).jpg|right]]主演的《[[超人：钢铁之躯|超人：钢铁之躯]]》是至今超人系列电影中票房最高的作品]]
{{main|超人：钢铁之躯}}
2008年6月，华纳兄弟公司联系了多位漫画作家、编剧和导演一起研究应该如何成功地重启超人系列电影<ref>{{cite news | author = Josh Wigler | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131203033434/http://splashpage.mtv.com/2009/03/26/mark-millar-on-his-superman-movie-trilogy-nothing-is-happening/ | url = http://splashpage.mtv.com/2009/03/26/mark-millar-on-his-superman-movie-trilogy-nothing-is-happening/ | title = Mark Millar On His 'Superman' Movie Trilogy: 'Nothing Is Happening' | work = MTV News | date = 2009-03-26 | accessdate = 2014-08-27 | archivedate = 2013-12-03 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。“我告诉他们这是个不错的点子，只管像看待[[李安|李安]]的《[[绿巨人_(电影)|绿巨人]]》一样来看待《超人归来》。”漫画小说作家马克·韦德（{{lang|en|Mark Waid}}）说，“《[[无敌浩克|无敌浩克]]》已经证明，观众会原谅你，他们也愿意接受新的版本”<ref name="Jen">{{cite news | author = Jennifer Vineyard | title = How To Reboot The Superman Movie Franchise-Comic Writers Chime In | publisher = MTV | date = 2008-08-11 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131013052908/http://splashpage.mtv.com/2008/08/11/how-to-reboot-the-superman-movie-franchise-comic-writers-chime-in/ | url = http://splashpage.mtv.com/2008/08/11/how-to-reboot-the-superman-movie-franchise-comic-writers-chime-in/ | accessdate = 2014-08-27 | archivedate = 2013-10-13 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。漫画小说作家格兰特·莫里森、高夫·强斯和布拉德·梅特泽都对电影的重启给出了自己的想法。莫里森的构思与他创作的《全明星超人》类似，而韦德的方案则与《超人：与生俱来的权利》接近<ref name="Jen" />。马克·米勒和导演[[马修·沃恩|马修·沃恩]]还计划了一套长达8个小时的三部曲，每一年发行一部，与《指环王》三部曲相似<ref>{{cite news | author = Martin Anderson | title = The Den Of Geek interview: Mark Millar | publisher = DenofGeek.com | date = 2008-07-20 | url = http://www.denofgeek.com/books-comics/11302/the-den-of-geek-interview-mark-millar | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131021033455/http://www.denofgeek.com/books-comics/11302/the-den-of-geek-interview-mark-millar | accessdate = 2014-08-27 | archivedate = 2013-10-21 | deadurl = yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | author = Josh Wigler | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140309125333/http://splashpage.mtv.com/2010/03/26/matthew-vaughn-superman/ | archivedate = 2014-03-09 | url = http://splashpage.mtv.com/2010/03/26/matthew-vaughn-superman/ | title = Matthew Vaughn Says 'Superman' Movie Discussions Were 'Very Brief' | work = MTV News | date = 2010-03-26 | accessdate = 2014-08-27 }}</ref>。米勒则建议以《教父》三部曲的模式来设计剧情，即包含有超人早期在氪星出生和成长，到最终失去超强力的一生写照<ref>{{cite news | author =  | title = Exclusive: Mark Millar Talks Superman | publisher = EmpireOnline | date = 2008-10-29 | url = http://www.empireonline.com/news/story.asp?NID=23521 | accessdate = 2014-08-27 | archivedate = 2013-11-02 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131102103809/http://www.empireonline.com/news/story.asp?NID=23521 }}</ref>。2009年8月，法院裁决杰里·西格尔一家人重新获得超人的电影版权<ref>{{cite news | author = Marc Graser | title = Superman co-creator's family given rights | publisher = Variety | date = 2009-08-13 | url = http://variety.com/2009/film/news/superman-co-creator-s-family-given-rights-1118007269/ | accessdate = 2014-08-27 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140827104828/http://variety.com/2009/film/news/superman-co-creator-s-family-given-rights-1118007269/ | archivedate = 2014-08-27 | deadurl = no }}</ref>，同时也认定华纳兄弟公司没有因拍摄之前的超人系列电影而欠下西格尔一家任何专利费用，但是如果新版的超人电影一直到2011年还没有开拍，那么西格尔就可以再以未拍摄电影的利润损失为由起诉华纳兄弟公司要求赔偿<ref>{{cite news | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140827104933/http://variety.com/2009/film/news/warner-bros-wins-superman-case-1118005806/ | archivedate = 2014-08-27 | url = http://variety.com/2009/more/news/warner-bros-wins-superman-case-1118005806/ | title = Warner Bros. wins 'Superman' case | author = McNary, Dave | date = 2009-07-08 | work = [[综艺_(杂志)|Variety]] | accessdate = 2014-08-27 }}</ref>。

2008年对《[[蝙蝠侠：黑暗骑士崛起|蝙蝠侠：黑暗骑士崛起]]》的故事进行探讨时，[[大卫·S·高耶|大卫·S·高耶]]得知华纳兄弟公司正在策划重启超人电影系列，于是把自己所构思的现代背景超人故事告知了[[克里斯托弗·诺兰|克里斯托弗·诺兰]]。诺兰对此留下了深刻的印象，并于2010年2月联系华纳兄弟公司提出了这一设想<ref>{{cite news | author = Staff | url = http://www.superherohype.com/news/102090-christopher-nolan-on-batman-and-superman | title = Christopher Nolan on Batman and Superman | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140827103715/http://www.superherohype.com/news/102090-christopher-nolan-on-batman-and-superman | deadurl = yes | publisher = Superhero Hype! | date = 2010-06-04 | accessdate = 2014-08-27 | archivedate = 2014-08-27 }}</ref>。考虑到《[[黑暗骑士|黑暗骑士]]》商业和评论上的成功<ref name="wall" />，华纳兄弟公司请诺兰来出任这部新电影的制片人，并由高耶编剧<ref>{{cite news |author=Finke, Nikki, and Mike Fleming |title=It's A Bird! It's A Plane! It's Chris Nolan! He'll Mentor Superman 3.0 And Prep 3rd Batman |publisher=Deadline.com |date=2010-02-09 |url=http://deadline.com/2010/02/its-a-bird-its-a-plane-its-chris-nolan-hell-mentor-superman-3-0-while-preparing-3rd-batman-24783/ |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5xLwx0v1Q?url=http://www.deadline.com/2010/02/its-a-bird-its-a-plane-its-chris-nolan-hell-mentor-superman-3-0-while-preparing-3rd-batman/ |archivedate=2011-03-21 |deadurl=yes |accessdate=2014-08-27 }}. .</ref>。诺兰也曾像1978年理查德·唐纳执导《超人》那样来为《[[蝙蝠侠诞生|蝙蝠侠诞生]]》选择演员，所以他也很赞赏辛格执导《超人归来》与老版电影联系起来的做法。“他们让白兰度、格伦·福特和尼德·巴蒂这些伟大的演员来扮演小角色，”诺兰表示，“这在当时的超级英雄电影中可是个不同寻常的做法”<ref>{{cite news | url = http://herocomplex.latimes.com/movies/christopher-nolan-takes-flight-with-superman-we-have-a-fantastic-story-1/ | title = Christopher Nolan takes flight with Superman: 'We have a fantastic story' [UPDATED] | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140721031557/http://herocomplex.latimes.com/movies/christopher-nolan-takes-flight-with-superman-we-have-a-fantastic-story-1/ | last = Boucher | first = Geoff | date = 2010-03-10 | work = Los Angeles Times | publisher =  | accessdate = 2014-08-27 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2014-07-21 }}</ref>。唐纳的电影也给童年时的诺兰留下了深刻的印象，还成为他用来判断电影质量好坏的试金石<ref>{{cite news | author = Rick Marshall | url = http://splashpage.mtv.com/2010/06/28/christopher-nolan-superman-actor/#more-36742 | title = Does Christopher Nolan Want An Unknown Actor For Next 'Superman' Movie? | work = MTV News | date = 2010-06-28 | accessdate = 2014-08-27 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140309141303/http://splashpage.mtv.com/2010/06/28/christopher-nolan-superman-actor/#more-36742 | deadurl = yes | archivedate = 2014-03-09 }}</ref>。[[吉尔莫·德尔·托罗|吉尔莫·德尔·托罗]]决定接拍小说《[[瘋狂山脈|瘋狂山脈]]》改编的同名电影，因此拒绝了执导本片的邀请<ref>{{cite news | author = Michael Fleming | url = http://deadline.com/2010/09/toronto-qa-julias-eyes-and-biutiful-producer-guillermo-del-toro-66712/ | title = Toronto Q&A: Guillermo Del Toro About Producing 'Julia's Eyes' And 'Biutiful' | work = Deadline.com | date = 2010-09-13 | accessdate = 2014-08-27 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140827105821/http://deadline.com/2010/09/toronto-qa-julias-eyes-and-biutiful-producer-guillermo-del-toro-66712/ | archivedate = 2014-08-27 | deadurl = no }}</ref>，之后公司还联系了[[罗伯特·泽米基斯|罗伯特·泽米基斯]]<ref>{{cite news | author = Josh Wigler | url = http://splashpage.mtv.com/2010/11/01/robert-zemeckis-superman-reboot/ | title = Robert Zemeckis On 'Superman' Reboot: 'I Passed On That Faster Than A Speeding Bullet' | work = MTV News | date = 2010-11-01 | accessdate = 2014-08-27 | archivedate = 2013-05-27 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130527062010/http://splashpage.mtv.com/2010/11/01/robert-zemeckis-superman-reboot }}</ref>。有传言称[[本·阿弗莱克|本·阿弗莱克]]曾考虑执导一部超人电影，他对此没有否认，不过也表示自己主要是基于故事情节来选择项目：“我所学到的一点是不要根据预算数额，或是花了多少钱在特技效果上以及在什么地方取景拍摄来看待一部电影，故事才是最重要的。”<ref>{{cite news | author = Michael Fleming | archivedate = 2014-08-27 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140827110038/http://deadline.com/2010/11/oscar-ben-affleck-qa-on-the-town-86778/ | deadurl = no | url = http://deadline.com/2010/11/oscar-ben-affleck-qa-on-the-town-86778/ | title = Oscar: Ben Affleck Q&A On 'The Town' | work = Deadline.com | date = 2010-11-26 | accessdate = 2013-05-25 }}</ref>此外，[[托尼·斯科特|托尼·斯科特]]、[[达伦·阿伦诺夫斯基|达伦·阿伦诺夫斯基]]、[[邓肯·琼斯|邓肯·琼斯]]（{{lang|en|Duncan Jones}}）、[[乔纳森·里贝斯曼|乔纳森·里贝斯曼]]和马特·里夫斯都曾是本片的导演人选<ref>{{cite news | author = Michael Fleming | url = http://deadline.com/2010/09/chris-nolan-looking-for-superman-director-69671/ | title = Chris Nolan Looking for 'Superman' Directors | work = Deadline.com | date = 2010-09-23 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140827110211/http://deadline.com/2010/09/chris-nolan-looking-for-superman-director-69671/ | accessdate = 2014-08-27 | archivedate = 2014-08-27 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。但最终华纳兄弟公司选中的是[[扎克·施奈德|扎克·施奈德]]，他于2010年10月加入剧组<ref>{{cite news | url = http://deadline.com/2010/10/zack-snyder-directing-superman-72340/ | title = SCOOP: Zack Snyder Directing 'Superman' | work = Deadline.com | author = Michael Fleming | date = 2010-10-04 | accessdate = 2014-08-27 | archivedate = 2014-08-27 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140827110327/http://deadline.com/2010/10/zack-snyder-directing-superman-72340/ }}</ref>。演员的敲定则在11月开始<ref>{{cite news | author = Mike Snider | url = http://content.usatoday.com/communities/gamehunters/post/2010/11/qa-screenwriter-david-goyer-on-call-of-duty-black-ops/1 | title = Q&A: Screenwriter David Goyer on 'Call of Duty: Black Ops' | work = USA Today | date = 2010-11-26 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140612163121/http://content.usatoday.com/communities/gamehunters/post/2010/11/qa-screenwriter-david-goyer-on-call-of-duty-black-ops/1 | archivedate = 2014-06-12 | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2014-08-27 }}</ref>，[[亨利·卡维尔|亨利·卡维尔]]出演超人<ref>{{cite news | author = Staff | url = http://www.superherohype.com/news/articles/125177-henry-cavill-to-play-superman?cpage=20#written_comments_title#.U_27fry_M5M | title = Henry Cavill to Play Superman!! | publisher = Superhero Hype! | date = 2011-01-30 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131018014229/http://www.superherohype.com/news/articles/125177-henry-cavill-to-play-superman?cpage=20#written_comments_title | accessdate = 2014-08-27 | archivedate = 2013-10-18 | deadurl = no }}</ref>，这让他成为了第一位出演这一角色的非美籍演员<ref>{{cite news | last = Saunders | first = Emma | url = http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-12333396 | title = BBC News — Film invasion of the Super-Brits | publisher = Bbc.co.uk | date = 2011-02-01 | accessdate = 2014-08-27 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120320184907/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-12333396 | archivedate = 2012-03-20 }}</ref>。[[艾米·亚当斯|艾米·亚当斯]]饰演路易斯·莱恩<ref>{{cite news | first = Sara | last = Vilkomerson | title = Amy Adams to play Lois Lane in 'Superman' | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140724045812/http://insidemovies.ew.com/2011/03/27/amy-adams-lois-lane-superman/ | work = [[娱乐周刊|Entertainment Weekly]] | date = 2011-03-27 | url = http://insidemovies.ew.com/2011/03/27/amy-adams-lois-lane-superman/ | accessdate = 2014-08-27 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2014-07-24 }}</ref>，[[黛安·蓮恩|黛安·蓮恩]]扮演玛莎·肯特。其他演员还包括[[凯文·科斯特纳|凯文·科斯特纳]]饰演乔纳森·肯特，[[迈克尔·珊农|迈克尔·珊农]]扮演大反派[[佐德将军|佐德将军]]，[[罗素·克劳|罗素·克劳]]诠释超人的生父，氪星人乔·艾尔<ref>{{cite news | author = Staff | date = 2011-06-15 | title = Russell Crowe Joins Superman 'Man of Steel': Playing Jor-El, Superman's Dad | work = Huffington Post | url = http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2011/06/15/russell-crowe-joins-superman-man-of-steel-jor-el_n_877642.html | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140412223050/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2011/06/15/russell-crowe-joins-superman-man-of-steel-jor-el_n_877642.html | accessdate = 2014-08-27 | archivedate = 2014-04-12 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。此外还有德国女演员安婕·特拉乌在片中出演另一位反派人物弗拉<ref>{{cite news | author = Adam B. Vary | title = Diane Lane will play Martha Kent in new "Superman" | work = [[娱乐周刊|Entertainment Weekly]] | url = http://insidemovies.ew.com/2011/03/02/diane-lane-martha-kent-superman/ | date = 2011-03-02 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131012232744/http://insidemovies.ew.com/2011/03/02/diane-lane-martha-kent-superman/ | accessdate = 2014-08-27 | archivedate = 2013-10-12 | deadurl = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | author = Staff | title = Kevin Costner Confirmed for Superman! | publisher = Superhero Hype! | date = 2011-03-18 | url = http://www.superherohype.com/news/128994-kevin-costner-confirmed-for-superman | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140827111052/http://www.superherohype.com/news/128994-kevin-costner-confirmed-for-superman | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2014-08-27 | accessdate = 2014-06-27 }}</ref>。电影的主体拍摄工作于2011年8月1日在[[伊利诺伊州|伊利诺伊州]]的[[芝加哥|芝加哥]]开始<ref name="ChicagoBusiness2">{{cite web | url = http://www.chicagobusiness.com/article/20110728/NEWS07/110729855/superman-flying-into-chicago-in-august-for-filming | first = Paul | last = Merrion | title = Superman flying into Chicago in August for filming | work = Crain's Chicago Business | date = 2011-07-28 | accessdate = 2014-08-27 | archive-date = 2011-08-18 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110818024029/http://www.chicagobusiness.com/article/20110728/NEWS07/110729855/superman-flying-into-chicago-in-august-for-filming | dead-url = no }}</ref>，2013年6月10日在纽约举行了[[首演|首映式]]<ref>{{cite web | title = 'Man of Steel' Premiere: Superman Takes Off in New York City | url = http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/gallery/man-steel-premiere-superman-takes-565807 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140704030431/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/gallery/man-steel-premiere-superman-takes-565807 | work = [[好莱坞报道|The Hollywood Reporter]] | accessdate = 2014-08-27 | date = 2013-06-11 | archivedate = 2014-07-04 | deadurl = no }}</ref>，多位演员出席<ref>{{cite web | last = McNary | first = Dave | url = http://variety.com/2013/film/news/man-of-steel-premiere-watch-the-live-stream-of-red-carpet-1200494957/ | title = Man of Steel Live Stream: Watch the Red Carpet Premiere | work = [[综艺_(杂志)|Variety]] | date = 2013-06-10 | accessdate = 2014-08-27 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131124033143/http://variety.com/2013/film/news/man-of-steel-premiere-watch-the-live-stream-of-red-carpet-1200494957/ | archivedate = 2013-11-24 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>，再于2013年6月14日全面上映，有传统2D、3D和[[IMAX|IMAX]]多种版本<ref>{{cite press release | url = http://www.marketwatch.com/story/man-of-steel-to-soar-into-theaters-next-summer-in-3d-2012-11-07 | title = "Man of Steel" to Soar into Theaters Next Summer in 3D | publisher = Marketwatch.com | date = 2012-11-07 | accessdate = 2014-08-27 | archivedate = 2013-10-17 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131017165140/http://www.marketwatch.com/story/man-of-steel-to-soar-into-theaters-next-summer-in-3d-2012-11-07 | deadurl = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | title = Third Batman, New Superman Part of IMAX Deal | publisher = Superhero Hype! | date = 2010-04-28 | url = http://www.superherohype.com/news/100703-third-batman-new-superman-part-of-new-imax-deal | accessdate = 2014-08-27 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140827112156/http://www.superherohype.com/news/100703-third-batman-new-superman-part-of-new-imax-deal | deadurl = yes | archivedate = 2014-08-27 }}</ref>。《超人：钢铁之躯》取得了商业上的成功，全球票房突破6.6亿美元，超过了之前任何一部超人系列电影。

=== 《蝙蝠侠大战超人：正义黎明》 ===
{{Main|蝙蝠侠大战超人：正义黎明}}
大卫·{{lang|en|S}}·高耶和扎克·施奈德分别是《超人：钢铁之躯》续集的编剧和导演<ref>{{cite web | last = Vejvoda | first = Jim | title = Zack Snyder, David Goyer Back for Man of Steel Sequel | accessdate = 2014-08-27 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140222130509/http://www.ign.com/articles/2013/06/11/zack-snyder-david-goyer-back-for-man-of-steel-sequel | url = http://www.ign.com/articles/2013/06/11/zack-snyder-david-goyer-back-for-man-of-steel-sequel | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2014-02-22 | publisher = [[IGN|IGN]] }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | author1 = Lucas Shaw | author2 = Brent Lang | url = http://www.thewrap.com/movies/article/man-steel-warner-bros-jeff-robinov-henry-cavill-97021/ | title = Why 'Man of Steel' Holds the Key to Warner Bros.' Future Franchises | date = 2013-06-12 | accessdate = 2014-08-27 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131227022012/http://www.thewrap.com/movies/article/man-steel-warner-bros-jeff-robinov-henry-cavill-97021 | work = The Wrap | archivedate = 2013-12-27 }}</ref>，但由于高耶还需要参加其它项目的制作，因《[[逃离德黑兰|逃离德黑兰]]》获[[奥斯卡金像奖|奥斯卡金像奖]]的编剧[[克里斯·泰瑞欧|克里斯·泰瑞欧]]获聘改写剧本<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/batman-superman-chris-terrio-write-666735 | title = Batman-Superman Film Enlists 'Argo' Writer (Exclusive) | work = [[好莱坞报道|The Hollywood Reporter]] | date = 2013-12-18 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140704002940/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/batman-superman-chris-terrio-write-666735 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2014-07-04 | accessdate = 2014-08-28 }}</ref>。克里斯托弗·诺兰也有望回归担任制片人，不过这次他发挥的作用会比上次要小<ref>{{cite web | title = ‘Man Of Steel’ Sequel Underway With Zack Snyder And David S. Goyer | url = http://deadline.com/2013/06/man-of-steel-sequel-underway-with-zack-snyder-and-david-s-goyer-517621/ | last = Finke | first = Nikki | date = 2013-06-10 | accessdate = 2014-08-27 | archivedate = 2014-08-27 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140827113618/http://deadline.com/2013/06/man-of-steel-sequel-underway-with-zack-snyder-and-david-s-goyer-517621/ }}</ref>。2013年6月16日，《[[华尔街日报|华尔街日报]]》报道称这部续集有可能在2014年上映<ref>{{cite web | last = Fritz | first = Ben | url = http://online.wsj.com/article/SB10001424127887323836504578549641408007794.html | title = 'Man of Steel' Movie May Give DC Comics More Superpowers | work = The Wall Street Journal | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130927120917/http://online.wsj.com/article/SB10001424127887323836504578549641408007794.html | date = 2013-06-16 | accessdate = 2014-08-27 | archivedate = 2013-09-27 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。华纳公司宣布，超人和蝙蝠侠将会在《超人：钢铁之躯》的续集中共同出场，影片计划于2015年上映<ref>{{cite web | url = http://herocomplex.latimes.com/movies/comic-con-2013-superman-batman-movie-will-follow-man-of-steel/ | title = Comic-Con 2013: ‘Superman & Batman’ movie will follow ‘Man of Steel’ | work = Los Angeles Times | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140708184039/http://herocomplex.latimes.com/movies/comic-con-2013-superman-batman-movie-will-follow-man-of-steel/ | archivedate = 2014-07-08 | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2014-08-27 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/superman-batman-film-set-comic-589521 | title = Superman & Batman Film Set for Comic-Con Reveal | work = [[好莱坞报道|The Hollywood Reporter]] | accessdate = 2014-08-27 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140531010813/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/superman-batman-film-set-comic-589521 | archivedate = 2014-05-31 }}</ref>。高耶在2013年[[圣地亚哥国际动漫展|圣地亚哥国际动漫展]]超人75周年活动中表示，续集的片名有可能是《超人大战蝙蝠侠》（{{lang|en|''Superman Vs Batman''}}）或《蝙蝠侠大战超人》（{{lang|en|''Batman Vs Superman''}}）<ref>{{cite web | title = Comic-Con: Man of Steel Sequel Likely Called Batman Vs. Superman | last = Collura | first = Scott | date = 2013-07-23 | accessdate = 2014-08-27 | archivedate = 2014-08-06 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140806165433/http://www.ign.com/articles/2013/07/23/comic-con-man-of-steel-sequel-likely-called-batman-vs-superman | url = http://www.ign.com/articles/2013/07/23/comic-con-man-of-steel-sequel-likely-called-batman-vs-superman }}</ref>。2013年8月22日，《[[娱乐周刊|娱乐周刊]]》报道称[[本·阿弗莱克|本·阿弗莱克]]将出演蝙蝠侠<ref>{{cite web | work = [[娱乐周刊|Entertainment Weekly]] | title = Ben Affleck is the new Batman | first = Lindsey | last = Bahr | date = 2013-08-22 | accessdate = 2014-08-27 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140704175350/http://insidemovies.ew.com/2013/08/22/ben-affleck-batman/ | deadurl = no | url = http://insidemovies.ew.com/2013/08/22/ben-affleck-batman/ | archivedate = 2014-07-04 }}</ref>。2013年12月4日，有报道称[[盖尔·加朵|盖尔·加朵]]将出演[[神力女超人_(DC漫画)|神力女超人]]<ref>{{cite web | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140714103202/http://variety.com/2013/film/news/gal-gadot-wonder-woman-batman-vs-superman-1200918310/ | url = http://variety.com/2013/film/news/gal-gadot-wonder-woman-batman-vs-superman-1200918310/ | title = Gal Gadot to Play Wonder Woman in ‘Batman vs. Superman’ | work = [[综艺_(杂志)|Variety]] | date = 2013-12-04 | accessdate = 2014-08-27 | archivedate = 2014-07-14 }}</ref>。此外，[[霍利·亨特|霍利·亨特]]将在片中扮演一名[[美国参议院|联邦参议员]]，[[冈本多绪|冈本多绪]]则会出演莱克斯·卢瑟的一名助手<ref>{{cite web | last = Bussey | first = Ben | title = Wolverine Actress Joins Batman V Superman - Yahoo Movies UK | publisher = Yahoo | date = 2011-04-20 | accessdate = 2014-08-27 | archivedate = 2014-07-15 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140715000525/https://uk.movies.yahoo.com/wolverine-actress-joins-batman-v-superman-153100173.html | url = https://uk.movies.yahoo.com/wolverine-actress-joins-batman-v-superman-153100173.html }}</ref>。[[卡兰·马尔韦|卡兰·马尔韦]]和[[斯科特·麦克纳里|斯科特·麦克纳里]]也获选参演，但具体角色不得而知<ref name="HunterMulveyOkamoto">{{cite web | title = Superman/Batman: Holly Hunter, Callan Mulvey, Tao Okamoto join cast | last = Breznican | first = Anthony | publisher = Entertainment Weekly | date = 2014-04-03 | accessdate = 2014-08-27 | url = http://insidemovies.ew.com/2014/04/03/supermanba