archive.org/web/20140605082918/http://www.mtv.com/news/1719411/amy-adams-on-wonder-woman-gal-gadot-too-skinny/ | title = Amy Adams Talks Back About Wonder Woman Body Shaming | author = Kase Wickman | archivedate = 2014-06-05 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | title = Jesse Eisenberg as Lex Luthor? A debate on Batman-Superman’s Villain | publisher = Variety | date = 2014-01-31 | accessdate = 2014-08-27 | archivedate = 2014-06-05 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140605082918/http://www.mtv.com/news/1719411/amy-adams-on-wonder-woman-gal-gadot-too-skinny/ | url = http://variety.com/2014/film/news/jesse-eisenberg-as-lex-luthor-miscast-or-inspired-choice-1201080207/ }}</ref>。影片计划在加拿大[[安大略|安大略]]的[[多伦多|多伦多]]进行拍摄<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.vancitybuzz.com/2013/07/man-of-steel-2-production-departs-vancouver-for-toronto/ | title = MAN OF STEEL 2 PRODUCTION DEPARTS VANCOUVER FOR TORONTO | publisher = Vancitybuzz.com | date = 2013-07 | accessdate = 2014-08-28 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131201080229/http://www.vancitybuzz.com/2013/07/man-of-steel-2-production-departs-vancouver-for-toronto/ | archivedate = 2013-12-01 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>，不过几位主要演员于2014年5月19日在[[密歇根州|密歇根州]][[底特律|底特律]]开始了主体拍摄工作<ref name="http://www.onlocationvacations.com">{{cite web | url = http://www.onlocationvacations.com/2014/05/16/batman-vs-superman-filming-location-in-birmingham-mi-first-set-photos-of-gal-gadot-zack-snyder/ | title = ‘Batman Vs. Superman’ filming location in Birmingham, MI & first set photos of Gal Gadot & Zack Snyder! | accessdate = 2014-08-28 | archivedate = 2014-05-17 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140517223244/http://www.onlocationvacations.com/2014/05/16/batman-vs-superman-filming-location-in-birmingham-mi-first-set-photos-of-gal-gadot-zack-snyder/ }}</ref><ref name="http://www.latinpost.com">{{cite web | archivedate = 2014-05-19 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140519055855/http://www.latinpost.com/articles/12293/20140511/batman-vs-superman-biggest-movie-filmed-in-michigan-ben-affleck-and-wife-jennifer-garner-expected-to-stay-in-detroit-during-production.htm | deadurl = no | url = http://www.latinpost.com/articles/12293/20140511/batman-vs-superman-biggest-movie-filmed-in-michigan-ben-affleck-and-wife-jennifer-garner-expected-to-stay-in-detroit-during-production.htm | title = 'Batman vs Superman' Biggest Movie Filmed in Michigan: Ben Affleck and Wife Jennifer Garner Expected to Stay in Detroit During Production | publisher = Latin Post | date = 2014-05-11 | accessdate = 2014-08-28 | author = Raymundo, Shawn }}</ref>，而涉及女演员[[盖尔·加朵|盖尔·加朵]]的戏份已在5月16日完成<ref name="http://ontheflix.com">{{cite web |archivedate=2014-07-05 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140705132511/http://ontheflix.com/2014/05/18/batman-vs-superman-gal-gadot-seen-filming-wonder-womandiana-prince-scenes-other-day/ |url=http://ontheflix.com/2014/05/18/batman-vs-superman-gal-gadot-seen-filming-wonder-womandiana-prince-scenes-other-day/ |title=Batman Vs Superman Gal Gadot Seen Filming Wonder Woman,Diana Prince Scenes Other Day |publisher=On the Flix |date=2014-05-18 |accessdate=2014-08-28 |author=Derek |deadurl=yes }}</ref>，影片还计划在[[摩洛哥|摩洛哥]]和南[[太平洋|太平洋]]取景<ref name="worldwide release">{{cite news | last = Derschowitz | first = Jessica | title = Batman vs. Superman film gets a title, new logo | url = http://www.cbsnews.com/news/batman-vs-superman-film-gets-a-title-new-logo/ | accessdate = 2014-08-28 | newspaper = CBS News | date = 2014-08-28 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140706220649/http://www.cbsnews.com/news/batman-vs-superman-film-gets-a-title-new-logo/ | archivedate = 2014-07-06 }}</ref>。
=== 《正義聯盟》（2017年） ===
{{main|正義聯盟 (電影)}}
2013年6月，據報導，[[大衛·S·高耶|大衛·S·高耶]]簽約編寫《蝙蝠俠對超人：正義曙光》以及新的《正義聯盟》劇本<ref name="Deadline.com (2013-06-10)"/>。2014年4月，[[查克·史奈德|查克·史奈德]]簽約回歸執導《正義聯盟》<ref name="Justice League-Snyder"/>。同年10月，華納兄弟宣布，該片的片名為《Justice League Part One》<ref name="EW (2014-10-15)"/>。2016年3月，據報導，華納兄弟聘請[[克里斯·泰瑞歐|克里斯·泰瑞歐]]擔任編劇，泰瑞歐表示，該片不會像《蝙蝠俠對超人：正義曙光》那麼黑暗<ref name="Justice League-Terrio"/>。6月，傑夫·強斯宣布，該片的片名簡化為《Justice League》 <ref name="Justice League-Title"/>。艾佛列克、卡維爾、賈多特、摩莫亞、費雪、艾恩斯、蓮恩、亞當斯、艾森柏格、尼爾森與萊特都將回歸飾演他們各自的角色<ref name="Justice League-Cast-1"/><ref name="Justice League-Cast-2"/>。[[希朗·漢德|希朗·漢德]]負責反派[[荒狼|荒狼]]的配音及動態捕捉<ref name="Justice League-Steppenwolf"/>。片中還包含數位首次登場的角色，如[[詹姆斯·高登_(漫畫)|詹姆斯·高登]]（[[J·K·西蒙斯|J·K·西蒙斯]]飾演）<ref name="Justice League-Gordon"/>、[[梅拉_(漫畫)|梅拉]]（[[安柏·赫德|安柏·赫德]]飾演）、{{link-en|努迪斯·武爾科|Nuidis Vulko}}（[[威廉·達佛|威廉·達佛]]飾演）<ref name="Justice League-Vulko"/>、{{link-en|愛瑞絲·威斯特·艾倫|Iris West Allen|愛瑞絲·威斯特}}（{{link-en|凱爾西·克萊蒙|Kiersey Clemons}}飾演）<ref name="Justice League-West"/>及亨利·艾倫（（{{lang|en|Henry Allen}}，[[比利·庫達普|比利·庫達普]]飾演）<ref name="Justice League-Allen"/>等。[[主體拍攝|主體拍攝]]於2016年4月11日至10月間進行，拍片地點包含[[華納兄弟利維斯登工作室|華納兄弟利維斯登工作室]]、英格蘭、倫敦及冰島<ref name="Justice League-filming-1"/><ref name="Justice League-filming-2"/>。2017年5月，導演史奈德因家庭因素而不得不退出電影的後製階段。[[喬斯·溫登|喬斯·溫登]]取代了史奈德的職務，連帶接手負責額外的補拍<ref name="Snyder family"/>。該片於2017年11月17日在全球上映<ref name="Justice League-filming-1"/>。

